\id MRK
\h MARK
\toc3 Mak
\toc2 Mark
\toc1 Mark Gelh Lungdamna Thu
\mt1 MARK
\mt2 Gelh Lungdamna Thu
\ili Laigelh: John Mark
\ili Laisim mite: Rome khua a thu-um mite
\ili A hun: A.D. 67-69
\imt1 Thu Mapi
\ip Topa Zeisu Khazih in leitung ah na a sep hun sung kum thum val deuh bek ahih hangin, tua hun sung teng in Zeisu Khazih in thu tamveipi hilhin na tuamtuam tampi sem hi. Kha Siangtho makaihna tawh Mark in Zeisu thuhilhna sangin a nuntakna, a nasepnate le a thuaknate na tamgen zaw hi. Tua ahih manin hih lai a sim masa Rome khua a thu-um mite nuntakna tawh kituak mahmah hi. A.D. 65 kum ciangin Rome khua a thu-um mite in bawlsiatna nakpitakin thuak uh hi. Mark in hih laibu a gelh hun pen A.D. 67-69 hi kha ding hi. Khazih in gimthuakna tungah a gualzopa ahihna hih laibu in gen ahih manin, a sim Rome thu-um mite, hih laibu in hehnem in thapia hi.
\ip Mark pen khat veivei John zong kici hi (\xt Saw 12:12\xt*). Pawlpi piantung lai in thu-um mite in Jerusalem khua a om Mark nu Mary inn ah kikhawm uh hi (\xt Saw 12:12\xt*). Paul le Barnabas gammial nasep khatvei khualzinna ah Mark in zong zui a (\xt Saw 13:4-12\xt*), ahi zongin tua khualzinna pan a sawt loin ciahkik hi (\xt Saw 13:13\xt*). Paul in a gammial nasep nihvei khualzinna ah tonpih nuam lo a, ahih hangin Barnabas in a tupa Mark tonpih nuam hi. Tua ahih manin Barnabas in Mark zawn in Cyprus tuikulh lamah pai uh a, Paul in Silas zawn in mundang khat ah zin uh hi (Saw 15:3-40). Ahi zongin Mark pen nasepna ah a kizang thei mahmah mi hoih khat hong suak hi. Tua mah bangin Paul in zong amah pahtawina thute na gen hi (\xt 2Ti 4:11\xt*).
\ip Mark in a laigelh lungdamna thubu pen khen nihin khen hi. A lian \xt 1:1-8:30\xt* in Zeisu Khazih thuneihna hong lak hi. Mark in Topa Zeisu nalamdang bawl sawm le giat na ciamteh in, a tamzaw pen hih khen masa sungah kimu thei hi. Khazih in nuntakna khempeuh tungah thunei ahihlam hong lak hi. A lian \xt 8:31-16:20\xt* sungah Topa Zeisu sihna, kivuina, thawhkikna cihte kimu thei hi. Hih Mark laibu sungah “Mihing Tapa” cih kammal sawm le nihvei kimu hi. Tua thu in Zeisu thuneihna, Pasian le mihing ahihna hong lakkhawm hi. Ahi zongin Mark Lai Siangtho sungah Mihing Tapa pen, “Midangte na a sepsak ding leh a nuntakna pia in mi tampi a tankhia dinga hong pai ahi hi,” ci ahih manin, a thuak dinga hong pai ahihlam kimu thei hi (\xt 10:45\xt*).
\ip Zeisu in a nungzuite aa dingin a thuak mah bangin, amah a zuite in zong amah bangin a thuak dingin a sap ahi hi. Amah in thuakna panin gualzawhna a ngah mah bangin, a mite zong tua mah bangin hong zawhpih ding hi.
\iot Tomlakna:
\io1 I. Nuntakna tungah Khazih thuneihna (\ior 1:1-8:30\ior*)
\io1 II. Khazih sihna, kivuina le thawhkikna (\ior 8:31-16:20\ior*)
\c 1
\s1 Tuiphumpa John Nasepna
\r Mat 3:1-12; Luk 3:1-20; Joh 1:6-8, 15-37
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 1:1 \xt Mat 4:3\x*Pasian Tapa Zeisu Khazih lungdamna thu a kipatna in hih bang ahi hi.
\v 2 \x + \xo 1:2 \xt Mat 11:10; Luk 7:27\x*Kamsangte laibu sungah,
\b
\q1 “\qt En in, nangma lampi a sialkhol dingin,\qt*
\q1 \qt Na mai ah ka kamtaipa ka sawl hi.\qt*\f + \fr 1:2 \ft \+xt Mal 3:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\q1
\v 3 \x + \xo 1:3 \xt Joh 1:23\x*\qt Gamlak a kikopa awging in,\qt*
\q1 \qt ‘Topa pai nading lam na sial unla,\qt*
\q1 \qt Ama lampite na tangsak un,’ a ci hi,\qt*”\f + \fr 1:3 \ft \+xt Isa 40:3\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\m ci in a kigelh hi.
\b
\p
\v 4 \x + \xo 1:4 \xt Mat 3:1; Luk 1:77; Joh 1:26, 33; Saw 1:5, 22\x*John in gamlak ah mite tuiphum a, mawh maisak nadingin kisikkikna thu tawh kisai tuiphumna thu a hilh hi.
\v 5 Tua ciangin Jerusalem khua mite a kipan Judea gama om mi khempeuh ama kiangah hong pai in a mawhnate uh pulak uh a, John in Jordan Gun ah amaute a tuiphum hi.
\v 6 \x + \xo 1:6 \xt Siam 11:22; 2Ku 1:8\x*Tu in John in kalaoh mul kigan puan silhin, savun kawnggak tawh a kawng gak a, \w kauphe\w* le gamlak khuaizu tawh a kivak hi.
\v 7 \x + \xo 1:7 \xt Saw 13:25\x*Amah in, “Kei sanga a vanglian zaw khat hong pai lai ding hi. Kunsuk a a khedapkhau sut ding nangawn in ka kilawm kei hi.
\v 8 \x + \xo 1:8 \xt Isa 44:3; Joe 2:28; Joh 1:33; Saw 1:5\x*En in keimah in note tui ah kong phum a, ahih hangin amah in note Kha Siangtho tawh hong phum ding hi,” ci in a hilh hi.
\s1 John In Zeisu Tuiphum
\r Mat 3:13-17; Luk 3:21-22; Joh 1:31-34
\p
\v 9 \x + \xo 1:9 \xt Mat 2:23; 3:1\x*Tua hun laitakin Galilee gam Nazareth khua panin Zeisu hong pai a, John in Jordan Gun sungah a tuiphum hi.
\v 10 \x + \xo 1:10 \xt Joh 1:32\x*Tuisung pan a hong paikhiat phetin van kihong a, Kha in vakhu bangin ama tungah hong kumsuk John in a mu hi.
\v 11 \x + \xo 1:11 \xt Mat 3:17\x*Tua ciangin van panin aw khat hong ging a, “Nangmah in hong lungdamsak mahmah ka it ka Tapa na hi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Satan In Zeisu Ze-et
\r Mat 4:1-11; Luk 4:1-13
\p
\v 12 Tua khit phetin Kha in gamlak ah Zeisu a sawlkhia pah hi.
\v 13 \x + \xo 1:13 \xt Pai 24:18; Mat 4:10; Heb 4:15\x*Gamlak ah ni 40 sung Zeisu omin \w Satan\w* ze-etna thuak a, gamsate tawh a omkhawm hi. Tua khit ciangin vantungmite in amah a kem uh hi.
\s1 Zeisu A Nasep Kipan
\r Mat 4:13-17; Luk 4:14-15
\p
\v 14 \x + \xo 1:14 \xt Mat 3:1; 4:12, 23\x*Thong sungah John a kikhum khit ciangin Galilee gam ah Zeisu pai in Pasian kumpigam tawh kisai lungdamna thu a tangko in ah,
\v 15 \x + \xo 1:15 \xt Joh 3:15; Rom 5:6; Gal 4:4; Eph 1:10\x*“A hun hong tung zo a, Pasian kumpigam hong tung dekta hi. Na mawhna uh kisikkik unla lungdamna thu um un,” ci in a gen hi.
\s1 Nungzui Masate Kisam
\r Mat 4:18-22; Luk 5:1-11
\p
\v 16 Galilee tuili gei ah Zeisu a pai laitakin Simon le a sanggampa Andrew a mu hi. Amaute ngabeng mi ahih manun tuili ah ngen khuhin a om uh hi.
\v 17 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Ka nung hong zui un, note mi mante kong suaksak ding hi,” a ci hi.
\v 18 \x + \xo 1:18 \xt Mat 4:19\x*Amaute in thakhatin a ngen uh nusia in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi.
\p
\v 19 Tua mun pan tawmvei sung a pai khit uh ciangin Zebedee tate ahi James le a sanggampa John zong a mu hi. Amaute gunkuang sungah ngen khui a om a mu hi.
\v 20 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute a sam pah hi. Amaute in a cial uh nasemte le a pa uh Zebedee gunkuang sungah nusia in Zeisu nung a zui uh hi.
\s1 Dawigilo Kihawlkhia
\r Luk 4:31-37
\p
\v 21 \x + \xo 1:21 \xt Mat 4:23\x*Tua khit ciangin amaute Capernaum khua ah pai uh a, \w Sabbath\w* ni ciangin \w kikhopna inn\w* ah Zeisu lut pahin thu a hilh hi.
\v 22 \x + \xo 1:22 \xt Mat 7:28-29\x*Amah in \w thukhamhilh siate\w* hilh bangin hilh loin thuneipa bangin hilh ahih manin a thuhilhna lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi.
\v 23 Tu in amaute kikhopna inn sungah dawi gilo a vei mi khat a om hi.
\v 24 \x + \xo 1:24 \xt Thuk 13:5; Lat 16:10; Mat 8:29; Luk 24:19; Joh 1:45-46; Saw 4:10; 1Jn 2:20\x*Amah kiko in, “Nazareth khua mi Zeisu aw, kote hong hi ci omsak lel in! Nang tawh bang kisai ka hi uh hiam? Kote a susia dinga hong pai na hi hiam? Kua na hi hiam cih kong thei uh a, Pasian mi Siangthopa na hi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 25 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Pau kei in, ama sung pan paikhia in!” ci in a taii hi.
\p
\v 26 Dawigilo in zong tua pa kongkawsak a, tua khit ciangin nakpitakin kiko a, tua pa sung pan a paikhia hi.
\v 27 Tua ciangin amaute khempeuh in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Bang thu bang la hi zawzen hiam? Hih thuhilhna thak a bangci thu hi peuhmah hiam? Thuneihna tawh amah in dawi gilote thu a piak ciangin ama thuthu a mang uh hi,” ci in khat le khat a kidong uh hi.
\p
\v 28 \x + \xo 1:28 \xt Mat 9:26\x*Tua khit ciangin Galilee gam kim le pam tengah ama thu a kizel pah hi.
\s1 Zeisu In Peter Sunghnu Damsak
\r Mat 8:14-15; Luk 4:38-39
\p
\v 29 Tu in kikhopna inn pan a paikhiat khit phetun Simon le Andrew inn sungah James le John tawh Zeisu a lut hi.
\v 30 Simon sunghnu nattun in lum ahih manin Zeisu kiangah a ko pah uh hi.
\v 31 \x + \xo 1:31 \xt Luk 7:14\x*Tua ciangin amah hong pai in tua nu a khut lenin a phot leh a cisa bei pahin tua nu in amaute zin a do hi.
\s1 Zeisu In Mi Tampi Damsak
\r Mat 8:16-17; Luk 4:40-41
\p
\v 32 \x + \xo 1:32 \xt Mat 4:24\x*Nitak lam ni a tum khit ciangin cina khempeuh le dawilut mite Zeisu kiangah hong puak uh hi.
\v 33 Tua khit ciangin a khuazang un kongpi gei ah hong kikhawm ngeingai uh a,
\v 34 \x + \xo 1:34 \xt Mat 4:23; Saw 16:17-18\x*Zeisu in natna tuamtuam a vei mi tampi damsak in dawi tampi a hawlkhia hi. Dawite in Zeisu thei uh ahih manin amah in amaute kam khat beek a pausak kei hi.
\s1 Zeisu In Gamdai Ah Thungen
\p
\v 35 \x + \xo 1:35 \xt Luk 3:21\x*Zingsang khua a vak ma in Zeisu tho a, gamdaihna mun khat ah pai in thu a ngen hi.
\v 36 Tua kalin Simon le a lawmte in amah a zong uh hi.
\v 37 Amaute in Zeisu a muh uh ciangin ama kiangah, “Mi khempeuh in nang hong zong uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 38 \x + \xo 1:38 \xt Isa 61:1\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Thu ka hilh theih nadingin hih kima om khua dangdangte ah zong pai ni; banghang hiam cihleh hih na sem ding maha hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 39 \x + \xo 1:39 \xt Mat 4:23-24\x*Tua bangin Galilee gam amaute kikhopna inn khempeuh ah thu hilhin dawite a hawlkhia hi.
\s1 Miphak Khat Kidamsak
\r Mat 8:2-4; Luk 5:12-14
\p
\v 40 Tua laitakin miphak khat Zeisu kiangah hong pai a, Zeisu mai ah khukdin in, “Hong damsak nuam lecin nong damsak thei hi,” ci in a thum hi.
\p
\v 41 Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa hehpihhuai sa ahih manin a khut zanin lawng a, “Kong damsak nuam hi. Damta in,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 42 Tua bang a cih khit phetin thakhatin tua pa tung panin phaknatna paikhia in a dam pah hi.
\v 43 Zeisu in tua pa khauhtakin thu a piak khit ciangin ciahsak pah a,
\v 44 \x + \xo 1:44 \xt Siam 13:49; Mat 8:4\x*“Hih thu kuama kiangah gen peuhmah kei in. Ahi zongin, pai inla siampipa kiangah va kilak in. Damna ngah na hih manin Moses hong thupiak bangin biakna va pia in. Tua in amaute tungah teci a suak ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 45 \x + \xo 1:45 \xt Luk 5:15-16; Joh 6:2\x*Ahih hangin tua pa paikhia in tua thu genthang in a kizelsak mang hi. Tua ahih manin Zeisu a kilangin khua sungah lut thei nawn lo a, khuanawl gamlak peuhah om hi napi mun khempeuh panin mite in ama kiang hong zuan veve uh hi.
\c 2
\s1 Pumzaw Mi Khat Kidamsak
\r Mat 9:2-8; Luk 5:18-26
\p
\v 1 Tua khit a sawt loin Capernaum khua ah Zeisu paikik a, amah inn sungah om hi cih thu mite in a za uh hi.
\v 2 Kongkhak gei dong nangawn ah om nading om lo zahdong in mi tampi thakhatin hong kikhawm uh a, Zeisu in amaute thu a hilh hi.
\v 3 \x + \xo 2:3 \xt Mat 4:24\x*Tua laitakin mi li in pumzaw mi khat hong zawng uh a, ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi.
\v 4 Mi honpi hangin amaute in Zeisu kiang naih thei lo uh ahih manin ama omna tungsan innkhum phelkhia in tua panin pumzawpa a lupna tawh a khaisuk uh hi.
\v 5 \x + \xo 2:5 \xt Luk 7:48\x*Zeisu in amaute upna a muh ciangin pumzawpa kiangah, “Ka ta aw, na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 6 Tua laitak a tu \w thukhamhilh siate\w* pawlkhat in amaute lungsim sungah,
\v 7 \x + \xo 2:7 \xt Isa 43:25\x*“Banghang in hihpa in hih bangin \w Pasian tungah pausia\w* ahi hiam? Pasian longal kua in mawhna maisak thei ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 8 Ahih hangin tua banga a ngaihsut lam uh Zeisu in a lungsim sungah thei pah a, “Banghang in tua bangin na lungsim sungah ngaihsun na hi uh hiam?
\v 9 Pumzawpa kiangah, ‘Na mawhnate hong kimaisak zo hi,’ cih ding leh, ‘Tho in, na lupna pua inla lampai in,’ cih ding koi baih zaw ahi hiam?
\v 10 \x + \xo 2:10 \xt Mat 8:20\x*Ahi zongin \w Mihing Tapa\w* in leitung ah mawhmaisak theihna thuneihna a neih lam na theih nading uh ahi hi,” a cih khit ciangin pumzawpa kiangah,
\v 11 “Tho in, na lupna pua inla na inn ah ciahin kong ci hi,” ci in a sawl hi.
\v 12 \x + \xo 2:12 \xt Mat 9:8, 33\x*Tua pa thakhatin tho a, a lupna pua in amaute khempeuh muhin a paikhia hi. Tua mite khempeuh in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hih bang mahmah khatvei beek i mu ngei kei hi!” ci in Pasian a phat uh hi.
\s1 Levi A Kisapna
\r Mat 9:9; Luk 5:27, 28
\p
\v 13 \x + \xo 2:13 \xt Luk 5:15; Joh 6:2\x*Tua khit ciangin tuili gei ah Zeisu paikhiakik in ama kiangah mipi khempeuh hong kikhawm uh a, amah in amaute thu a hilh hi.
\v 14 \x + \xo 2:14 \xt Mat 4:19\x*Amah lam a pai laitakin Alphaeus tapa Levi \w siah\w*donna buuk sungah tu a om a muh ciangin, “Hong zui in,” a ci hi. Tua ciangin Levi zong dingto in a zui hi.
\p
\v 15 Tu in, Levi inn ah an ne dingin Zeisu a tut laitakin, \w siahdongte\w* le mawhneite tampitak in zong Zeisu le a nungzuite tawh ankuang a umkhawm uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh tualai ah tua bang mi tampi in amah a zui uh hi.
\v 16 \x + \xo 2:16 \xt Mat 9:11\x*\w Pharisee\w* pawlte le thukhamhilh siate in siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm in a om Zeisu a muh uh ciangin a nungzuite kiangah, “Banghang in amah in siahdongte le mawhneite tawh an nekhawm ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 17 \x + \xo 2:17 \xt Luk 19:10; 1Ti 1:15\x*Zeisu in tua thu a zak ciangin amaute kiangah, “Cidamte in siavuan kisam lo uh a, cinate bekin kisam uh hi. Mi dikte sam dinga hong pai ka hi kei a, mawhneite a kisikkik nadingun a sam dingin hong pai ka hi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Antanna Thu
\r Mat 9:14-17; Luk 5:33-39
\p
\v 18 \x + \xo 2:18 \xt Mat 6:16-18; Saw 13:2\x*John nungzuite le Phariseete nungzuite in an a tang uh hi. Tua khit ciangin amaute Zeisu kiangah pai uh a, “John nungzuite le Phariseete nungzuite in antang napi uh banghang in na nungzuite in antang lo uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi.
\p
\v 19 Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Zineipa in a lawm a gualte a ompih laitakin amaute in antang thei ding uh ahi hiam? A ompih laiteng an a tang thei kei ding uh hi.
\v 20 \x + \xo 2:20 \xt Luk 17:22\x*Ahih hangin zineipa a kilakkhiat hun hong tung ding a, tua hun ciangin amaute in an a tang ding uh hi.
\p
\v 21 “Kuamah in puan lui kek a ton nai lo puan thak tawh a phop kei hi. Tua bangin phop leh puan thak in puan lui kaikek in, a kekna a zai semsem ding hi.
\v 22 Kuamah in savun um lui sungah lenggahzu thak a thun kei uh hi. Tua bangin kithun leh lenggahzu thakin savun um lui phukham in lenggahzu teng buakhia ding a, savun um lui zong a kisia ding hi. Lenggahzu thak pen savun um thak sunga thun ding ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Sabbath Ukpa
\r Mat 12:1-8; Luk 6:1-5
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 2:23 \xt Thu 23:25\x*Tu in \w Sabbath\w* ni in buhlei kantanin Zeisu a pai laitakin a nungzuite in buhvuite a zut uh hi.
\v 24 \x + \xo 2:24 \xt Mat 12:2\x*Tua ciangin Phariseete in ama kiangah, “En in, banghang in Sabbath ni in amaute in thukham tawh kituak loin gamta uh ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 25 Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Siampi Abiathar a khanlai in, David le a lawmte gilkial in a cimawh ngei uh hi.
\v 26 \x + \xo 2:26 \xt Siam 24:5-9; 1Sa 21:1-6; 2Sa 8:17; 1Kh 24:6\x*Tua ciangin amah Pasian inn sungah lutin siampite longal midangte nek theih ding a hi lo Ompihna Anlumte ne in, a lawmte zong a piak thu sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 27 \x + \xo 2:27 \xt Pai 23:12; Thu 5:14; Col 2:16\x*Tua ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “Sabbath ni pen mite aa dinga kibawl hi a, mite pen Sabbath ni aa dinga kibawl hi lo hi.
\v 28 \x + \xo 2:28 \xt Mat 8:20\x*Tua ahih manin Mihing Tapa in Sabbath Ukpa zong ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\c 3 
\s1 Sabbath Ni A Cidamsakna 
\r Mat 12:9-13; Luk 6:6-10 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 3:1 \xt Mat 4:23\x*Tua khit ciangin \w kikhopna inn\w* sungah Zeisu lutkik a, tualai ah khut langkhat a si mi khat a om hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 3:2 \xt Mat 12:10\x*Tua ciangin amaute in Zeisu a mawhmat theih nadingun \w Sabbath\w* ni in tua mipa a damsak peuhmah hiam ci in a en gige uh hi. 
\v 3 Zeisu in a khut a sipa kiangah, “Ding inla, hong pai in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Sabbath ni in a pha bawlhuai hiam a sia bawlhuai hiam? Nuntakna khat hotkhiathuai hiam thahhuai hiam?” ci in a dong hi. Ahih hangin amaute pau loin a dai khipkhep uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 Amaute lungkhauhna hangin Zeisu in heh le dah thuah a, a kim a pam teng a ban et khit ciangin tua mipa kiangah, “Na khut zan in,” ci in a sawl hi. 
\p Amah in a zan leh a langkhat lam mah bangin a dam hi. 
\v 6 \x + \xo 3:6 \xt Mat 22:16\x*Tua ciangin \w Pharisee\w* pawlte paikhia in Herod pawlte tawh amah a suksiat theih nading uh thakhatin a vaihawm uh hi. 
\s1 Mi honpi In Zeisu Zui 
\r Mat 12:14-16 
\p 
\v 7 \x + \xo 3:7 \xt Mat 4:25\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu a nungzuite tawh tuili lamah kihemkhia a, Galilee le Judea pana hong pai mi honpi in amah a zui uh hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 3:8 \xt Mat 11:21\x*Jerusalem khuapi, Idumia gam Jordan Gun galkhat pan le Tyre le Sidon khuakim panin mi tampite in Zeisu nasep tampite a zak uh ciangin ama kiangah a hong pai uh hi. 
\v 9 Tua ciangin mi honpite in amah a phut khak loh nadingin gunkuang neu khat ama aa dingin a koihkholh nadingun a nungzuite a sawl hi. 
\v 10 \x + \xo 3:10 \xt Mat 4:23; 9:20\x*Banghang hiam cihleh amah in mi tampi damsak ahih manin cina luna a om zahzah amah lawng kha nuamin a kiphu gawp uh hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 3:11 \xt Mat 4:3\x*Dawigilote in amah a muh uh ciangin, a mai ah pukin, “Nang in Pasian Tapa na hi hi,” ci in a kiko uh hi. 
\v 12 \x + \xo 3:12 \xt Mat 8:4; Saw 16:17-18\x*Ahi zongin, Zeisu in ama thu kuamah a theihsak loh nading uh khauhtakin a kham hi. 
\s1 Sawltak Sawm Le Nih Kiteel 
\r Mat 10:1-4; Luk 6:13-16 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 3:13 \xt Mat 5:1\x*Zeisu in mual tung ah kahto in ama mi deih teng sam a, amaute zong ama kiangah a hong pai uh hi. 
\v 14 Tua khit ciangin amah in amah tawh a omkhawm ding le thuhilh a a sawlkhiat theih ding mi sawm le nih a seh hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 3:15 \xt Mat 10:1\x*Natna a damsak theih nading uh le dawite a hawlkhiat theih nadingun thuneihna a pia hi. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 3:16 \xt Joh 1:42\x*Tua mite in, Zeisu in Peter ci a, min thak a phuahsakpa Simon, 
\v 17 Zebedee tapa James le ama min thak dingin “Vanging Tate” cih khiatna a nei Boanerges cih min a phuah Zebedee tapa James sanggampa John, 
\v 18 Andrew, Philip, Bartholomew, Matthew, Thomas, Alphaeus tapa James, Thaddaeus, Minamveipa Simon le 
\v 19 amah a lehhekpa Judas Iscariot ahi uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Le Beelzebub 
\r Mat 12:24-30; Luk 11:15-23 
\p Tua khit ciangin amaute inn khat ah a lut uh hi. 
\v 20 Tua ciangin mi honpite khatvei hong kikhawmkik uh ahih manin amaute in an nangawn ne man lo uh hi. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 3:21 \xt Joh 10:20; Saw 26:24\x*Ahih hangin ama innkuanpihte in hih thu a zak uh ciangin mi hai tawh kibang sa uh ahih manin a pummat dingin a kuan uh hi. 
\p 
\v 22 \x + \xo 3:22 \xt Mat 15:1; Joh 7:20\x*Jerusalem khuapi pana hong paisuk \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in, “Ama sungah \w Beelzebub\w* lut a, tua dawi mangpipa min suangin dawite a hawlkhia ahi hi,” a cihsan uh hi. 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 3:23 \xt Mat 4:10\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute samin thugentehna tawh thu a hilhin ah, “\w Satan\w* in bangci bangin Satan hawlkhia thei ding ahi hiam? 
\v 24 Gam khat peuhmah kiphelkhap leh tua gam ding zo lo ding hi. 
\v 25 Innkuan khat a kiphelkhap leh zong tua innkuan ding zo lo ding hi. 
\v 26 Satan amah le amah kido in kiphelkhap leh ding zo lo dinga beimang ding hi. 
\v 27 \x + \xo 3:27 \xt Isa 49:24-25\x*Mi thahatpa hencip masa loin kuamah in ama inn sungah lutin a neihsate a laksak zo kei ding hi. Amah a kihencip khit ciang bekin a inn a kiluh zo pan ding hi. 
\v 28 Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, mihingte mawhna khempeuh le Pasian tunga pausiatnate a kimaisak ding hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 3:29 \xt Mat 12:31-32; Luk 12:10\x*Ahih hangin Kha Siangtho tunga a pausiate cikmah hunin kimaisak lo ding a, tawntung gimna a thuak ding uh hi,” ci in a gen hi. 
\p 
\v 30 “Ama sungah dawigilo lut hi,” ci in ngawh uh ahih manin amah in hih thugentehna tawh a hilh ahi hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Nu Le A Sanggamte 
\r Mat 12:46-50; Luk 8:19-21 
\p 
\v 31 Tua laitakin a nu le a sanggamte ama kiangah hong pai uh a, amah a sam ding mi sawlin inn pualam ah a ngak uh hi. 
\v 32 Ama kimah mi honpite a tu uh hi. Amah a samte in, “En in, na nu le na sanggamte in nang tawh kimu nuamin innpua lamah om uh hi,” ci in a gen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 33 Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Ka nu le ka sanggamte kua ahi uh hiam?” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 34 Amah in a kianga tu mite gualet a, “En un, hih mite in ka nu le ka sanggamte ahi uh hi. 
\v 35 Banghang hiam cihleh Pasian deihna banga a gamtate peuhmah ka sanggampa, ka sanggamnu le ka nu ahi uh hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\c 4 
\s1 Khaici Vawhpa Thugentehna 
\r Mat 13:1-23; Luk 8:4-15 
\p 
\v 1 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in tuili gei ah thu a hilhkik hi. Mi honpite ama kiangah hong kikhawm uh ahih manin tui tunga om gunkuang sungah a tu hi. Mipi khempeuh in tuili lam nga in leilak ah a om uh hi. 
\v 2 Amah in thugentehna tawh thu tampi a hilhin ah, 
\v 3 “Ngai un! Khaici vawhpa khat khaici vawh dingin a kuankhia hi. 
\v 4 Khaici a vawh ciangin khaici pawlkhat lam gei ah tu a, vana vasate hong lengin a nemang uh hi. 
\v 5 Pawlkhatte leitang a tam lohna mun suang tungah tu a, lei a dai hangin a po pah hi. 
\v 6 Ahih hangin zungkha zo lo ahih manin ni hong suakin nisa in a kat ciangin a keumang uh hi. 
\v 7 Khaici pawlkhatte ling lakah tu a, lingkungte hong khangin depgawp ahih manin a gah zo kei uh hi. 
\v 8 \x + \xo 4:8 \xt Joh 15:5; Col 1:6\x*Ahi zongin khaici pawlkhatte leihoihna ah a tu hi. Tuate po in hong khang a, pawlkhatte a zah 30, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 100 a gah uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 4:9 \xt Mat 11:15\x*Tua ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Zeisu amah guak a om laitak, sawm le nihte le a kim a pama om mite in tua thugentehna thu a dong uh hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 4:11 \xt Mat 3:2; 1Co 5:12-13; Col 4:5; 1Th 4:12; 1Ti 3:7\x*Amah in amaute kiangah, “Pasian kumpigam thusimte note kong theisak hi. Ahih hangin a pualam mite tungah thu khempeuh thugentehna tawh ka hilh hi. 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 4:12 \xt Isa 6:9-10; Mat 13:13-15\x*“Tua in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Amaute in enen napi a muh theih loh nading,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Ngaingai napi a tel theih loh nading uh ahi hi.\qt* 
\q1 \qt Tua hi keileh amaute hong kihei kha ding uh a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A mawhnate uh kimaisak ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 4:12 \ft \+xt Isa 6:9-10\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* a cih thu a tangtun nading ahi hi,” 
\m ci in a dawng hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 13 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Note in hih thugentehna tel zo lo na hih uh leh thugentehna khempeuh koici tel zawh ding na hi uh hiam? 
\v 14 \x + \xo 4:14 \xt Luk 1:2; Saw 4:31; Phi 1:14\x*Khaici vawhpa in Pasian thu a vawh hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 4:15 \xt Mat 4:10\x*Mi pawlkhatte lam gei a a tu khaici tawh kibang uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin thakhatin \w Satan\w* hong pai in amaute lungsim sunga kivawhsa thu a lakkhiatsak hi. 
\v 16 Tua mah bangin pawlkhatte suang laka a tu khaici tawh kibang uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin lungdamtakin sang pah uh a, 
\v 17 zungkha lo uh ahih manin tawlkhat sung bek thuak zo uh a, Pasian thu hanga haksatna ahih keileh bawlsiatna hong tun ciangin a lungkia pah hi. 
\v 18 Tu in hihte in ling laka a tu khaicite ahi uh hi. Amaute in thu a za mite hi uh a, 
\v 19 \x + \xo 4:19 \xt Mat 19:23; 1Ti 6:9-10, 17; 1Jn 2:15-17\x*leitung nuntak nading lunghimawh in khemna tawh kidim na dang tuamtuamte a lunggulh mite ahi uh hi. Tua nate in a zaksa uh thu depgawp ahih manin a gah zo kei uh hi. 
\v 20 Ahi zongin hihte in lei hoihna ah a tu khaici ahi uh hi. Amaute in thu a zak uh ciangin sang uh a, pawlkhatte a zah 30, pawlkhatte a zah 60, pawlkhatte a zah 100 a gah uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Khosang Tunga Kivak Meivak 
\r Mat 5:15, 16; Luk 8:16-18; 11:33-36 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 4:21 \xt Mat 5:15\x*Amah in amaute kiangah a genbeh in ah, “Note in lawh a khuh ding le lupna nuai a koih ding peuhin meivak vak ngei na hi uh hiam? Meivak tunna tungah koih zaw hi lo na hi uh hiam? 
\v 22 \x + \xo 4:22 \xt Jer 16:17; Mat 10:26; Luk 8:17\x*Banghang hiam cihleh a kilang lo dinga a kiselsim thei bangmah om lo a, khuavak ah a kilang lo dingin a kiselcip thei bangmah om lo hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 4:23 \xt Mat 11:15\x*Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 4:24 \xt Mat 7:2\x*Tua ciangin amah in amaute tungah a genin ah, “Na thu zak uh limtakin ngaihsun un. Note zat seeng mah tawh no aa dingin hong kitehsakkik ding hi. Hih thu a za note tungah a tamzaw in a hong kipia ding hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 4:25 \xt Mat 25:29\x*Banghang hiam cihleh a neite kipiak beh ding a, a nei lote a neih sunsun nangawn a kilakkhiatsak ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Khaici Tawh Thugentehna 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 4:26 \xt Mat 13:24\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Pasian kumpigam in leilak ah khaici a vawh mipa tawh kibang hi. 
\v 27 Tua pa, sun tawh zan tawh ihmu zel, tho zel a, ama theih loh kalin khaici poin a khang hi. 
\v 28 Leitang in ama thu in gah a gahsak hi. A masa in hong ngum a, tua khit ciangin hong vui in a vui sungah a tak hong dim hi. 
\v 29 \x + \xo 4:29 \xt Kil 14:15\x*A min ciangin at hunta ahih manin a phiaukawi tawh a at pah hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Ankamtang Thugentehna 
\r Mat 13:31-33; Luk 13:18, 19 
\p 
\v 30 \x + \xo 4:30 \xt Mat 13:24\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Pasian kumpigam bang tawh kibang a, bang tawh genteh ding i hi hiam? 
\v 31 Pasian kumpigam in ankamtang tawh kibang hi. Ankamtang in lei ah a kivawh laitakin leitung a khaici khempeuh lakah a tang neupen hi a, 
\v 32 ahih hangin a kivawh khit ciangin a kung hong po in, khai kung khempeuh sangin golzaw a, a mengkhia a hiangte golpipi hong pha hi. Tua ciangin vana leng vasate in a hiang kawm ah bu a tom thei uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 4:33 \xt Joh 16:12\x*Amah in amaute theih zawh dingin tua bang thugentehna tampi tawh a hilh hi. 
\v 34 \x + \xo 4:34 \xt Joh 16:25\x*Amaute kiangah thugentehna loin thu a hilh kei hi. Ahih hangin ama nungzuite bek tawh a om ciangin thu khempeuh teltakin a hilh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In Huihpi Daisak 
\r Mat 8:23-27; Luk 8:22-25 
\p 
\v 35 Tua ni nitak lamin amah in a nungzuite kiangah, “Galkhat lamah galkah ni,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 36 Tu in amaute in mi honpite a nusiat khit uh ciangin Zeisu a na tuanna sa gunkuang tawh amah a paipih uh hi. Gunkuangneu dangte zong amaute tawh a paikhawm uh hi. 
\v 37 Tua laitakin huihpi nakpi in hong nung a, tuihual in gunkuang vatgawp ahih manin gunkuang tui sungah a tum dekdek hi. 
\v 38 Ahih hangin Zeisu in gunkuang taw lamah lukham khat kham in a ihmu hi. Tua ciangin a nungzuite in amah phong uh a, “Sia aw, simang khin le ung phamawh sa lo na hi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 39 Tua ciangin amah tho in huihpi taii a, tuipi kiangah, “Dai inla om hithiat in,” ci in thu a pia hi. Tua ciangin huihpi khawlin a dai dide pah hi. 
\p 
\v 40 \x + \xo 4:40 \xt Mat 14:31\x*Amah in amaute kiangah, “Banghang in hi zahtakin lau zawzen na hi uh hiam? Banghang in upna nei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 41 Amaute lau mahmah uh a, “Hihpa bangci bang mi hi zawzen ahi hiam? Huihpi le tuipite nangawn in a thu a mang tazen uh hi,” ci in khat le khat a kiho uh hi. 
\c 5 
\s1 Dawi Lutpa Khat Kidamsak 
\r Mat 8:28-34; Luk 8:26-40 
\p 
\v 1 Amaute in tuili galkhat a om Gadara mite teenna kuam a tung uh hi. 
\v 2 Gunkuang tung pan Zeisu a tuahkhiat ciangin dawigilo a vei mi khat han panin hong paikhia in thakhatin Zeisu a na dawntuah hi. 
\v 3 Tua pa han lakah teeng a, sikkhau nangawn tawh kuamah in a hen zo kei hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Banghang hiam cihleh sikkhau tawh tam veipi khih in kol a kibulh hangin a sikkhau bottat in a kol zong peksat a, kuamah in a zo zo kei hi. 
\v 5 Han lak le mual tung ah sun le zanin om tawntung a, kiko niloh in amah le amah suang tawh a kikuiliam gawp hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Tua pa in Zeisu a galmuh ciangin ama kiangah tai in a bia hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 5:7 \xt Mat 8:29; Heb 7:1\x*Amah nakpi in kiko a, “A Sangbel Pasian Tapa Zeisu aw, nang tawh ka kisaina bang om ahi hiam? Kei nong bawlsiat loh nadingin Pasian minin kong thum hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Banghang hiam cihleh Zeisu in, “Nang dawigilo aw, ama sung pan paikhia in,” ci in thu a pia zo hi. 
\p 
\v 9 Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Na min bang ahi hiam?” ci in a dot ciangin amah in, “Kote tampi ka hih manun ka min \w Legion\w* ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Zeisu in tua gam panin amah a hawlkhiat loh nadingin tua pa in nakpitakin a thum hi. 
\v 11 Tu in tua mun tawh a kinai mualte tungah vok honpi khat kicing in a om hi. 
\v 12 Tua ciangin dawi gilote khempeuh in Zeisu kiangah, “Vok honte sungah ka lut theih nadingun hong sawl in,” ci in a thum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Tua ciangin Zeisu in a phal pah hi. Dawigilote paikhia in vokte sungah a lut uh hi. Tua ciangin vok honte ken lakah taisuk gawp uh a, tui sung kidenna in a si khin uh hi. Tua vok honte 2,000 bang a pha hi. 
\p 
\v 14 Tua ciangin vok cingte tai pah vingveng uh a, khua sung le gam sung tengah hih thu a va gen uh ciangin tua thupiang en dingin khua mite a hong paikhia uh hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 5:15 \xt Mat 4:24\x*Zeisu kiangah a tun uh ciangin dawigilo legion khat a lutna mipa, puansilh in lungsim ngeina pua in tu hithiat a om a mu uh hi. Tua ciangin amaute a lau uh hi. 
\v 16 Dawi a lutna pa le vokte tunga thupiang a mu mite in tua khua mite kiangah a gensawn uh hi. 
\v 17 Tua khit ciangin tua gam panin Zeisu a paikhiat nadingin tua mite in a ngen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 18 Gunkuang sungah Zeisu a kah ciangin dawi a lutna mipa in Zeisu zui nuamin a kun hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 5:19 \xt Mat 8:4\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in sang loin ama kiangah, “Na inn ah ciah inla Topa in na lianpi hong bawlnate le hong hehpihnate na lawmte kiangah va gen in,” ci in a sawl hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 5:20 \xt Mat 4:25\x*Tua pa pai in Zeisu in ama tunga a bawl na lianpite \w Decapolis gam\w* sung tengah kizelsak a, mi khempeuh in lamdang a sa uh hi. 
\s1 Jairus Tanu Le Siluang Numei 
\r Mat 9:18-26; Luk 8:41-56 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 5:21 \xt Mat 9:1\x*Tu in gunkuang tungah Zeisu tuangin a gal khat ah a galkahkik khit ciangin mi honpite a hong kikhawm uh hi. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 5:22 \xt Luk 13:14; Saw 13:15\x*Amah tuili gei ah a om laitakin en in, \w kikhopna inn\w* ukte lakah Jairus kici mi khat hong pai a, Zeisu a muh ciangin a khephung ah bokin 
\v 23 \x + \xo 5:23 \xt Mat 19:13; Luk 4:40; Saw 6:6\x*nakpitak thum a, “Ka tanuno si dekdek hi. Amah cidam a hong nuntak theih nadingin hong pai inla a tungah na khut hong ngaksak in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 24 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amah zui a, mi honpi in zong Zeisu paina zui uh ahih manin a phu kha gawp uh hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 5:25 \xt Siam 15:25-30\x*Tualai ah kum sawm le kum nih sung siluang natna a vei numei khat a om hi. 
\v 26 Gimna tampi thuakin siavuan tampi zong kibawlsak a, a neihsa teng nangawn a beita hi. Ahih hangin noptuam cih thadah a gim zaw semsem hi. 
\v 27 Tua nu in Zeisu thu a zak ciangin mi honpi lakah hong lut a, a nung lam pan zuanin Zeisu puan a lawng hi. 
\v 28 \x + \xo 5:28 \xt Mat 9:20\x*Banghang hiam cihleh tua nu in, “A \w puan\w* va lawng beek leng zong ka dam ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 29 A lawn khit phetin tua nu a siluang kang pah a, a natna a dam lam ama sungah a kithei hi. 
\p 
\v 30 \x + \xo 5:30 \xt Luk 5:17\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in ama sung pan vangliatna paikhia hi cih thei in mi honpi lamah thakhatin kihei a, “Kua in ka puan hong lawng ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 31 Ahih hangin Zeisu nungzuite in ama kiangah, “Mi honpi in nang hong sukphut hong tophut cih thei napi cin, ‘Banghang in kua in hong lawng hiam?’ cimawk na hi hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 32 Zeisu in amah a lawng numeinu a muh nadingin a kim a pam teng a en kawikawi hi. 
\v 33 Tua nu in ama tunga thupiang khempeuh thei ahih manin laulua in a ling hi. Tua khit ciangin Zeisu kiangah hong pai in ama mai ah bok a, thupiang khempeuh ahi bangbang in a genkhia hi. 
\v 34 \x + \xo 5:34 \xt Mat 9:22; Saw 15:33\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Ka tanu aw, na upna in hong damsak zo hi. Lungnuamtakin ciah inla na natna dam tahen,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 35 Amah a paupau laitakin kikhopna inn ukpa inn pana hong paite hong tung uh a, “Na tanu si zo hi; banghang in Siapa buaisak lai ding na hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 36 Zeisu in tua thu a zak phetin kikhopna inn ukpa kiangah, “Patau kei inla um in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 37 \x + \xo 5:37 \xt Mat 4:21\x*Zeisu in Peter, James le a sanggampa John longal kuamah dang a kizuisak kei hi. 
\v 38 Tua ciangin kikhopna inn ukpa inn ah Zeisu a tun ciangin mite kap le mau a om ngeingai a mu hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 5:39 \xt Mat 9:24\x*Zeisu inn sungah luta amaute kiangah, “Banghang in mau in kap ngeingai na hi uh hiam? Numeino a si hi loin a ihmu ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 40 Tua ciangin tua mite in amah zahpihin a nuihsan uh hi. Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute a vekpi un pusuaksak a, numeino nu le pa le ama tonpih mite a sap khit ciangin numeino lupna inndei sungah a lut uh hi. 
\v 41 \x + \xo 5:41 \xt Luk 7:14\x*Tua ciangin amah in numeino khut len in, “Talitha, cumi,” a ci hi. A khiatna in, “Numeino aw, tho in kong ci hi,” a cihna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 42 Tua ciangin numeino thakhatin tho in lam a pai hi. Amah in kum sawm le kum nih a pha numeino ahi hi. Amaute in lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 5:43 \xt Mat 8:4\x*Ahih hangin tua thu kuamah a theihsak loh nadingun Zeisu in khauhtakin a kham hi. Tua khit ciangin numeino nek theih khatpeuh a piak nadingun a sawl hi. 
\c 6
\s1 Nazareth Khua Ah Zeisu Hawh
\r Mat 13:54-58
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 6:1 \xt Mat 2:23\x*Tua ciangin tua mun pan Zeisu paikhia in ama khankhiatna gam ah pai a, a nungzuite in a zui uh hi.
\v 2 \x + \xo 6:2 \xt Mat 4:23\x*\w Sabbath\w* ni hong tun ciangin \w kikhopna inn\w* sungah thu a hilh hi. Ama thuhilhna a za mi tampi in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Hihpa in hih thute koilai pana a ngah ahi hiam? A khut tawh hih bang nalamdang a bawl theih nadinga a kipia pilna in bangci bang pilna hi zawzen hiam?
\v 3 \x + \xo 6:3 \xt Mat 12:46; Joh 6:61\x*Amah in Mary tapa, khutsiampa hi lo ahi hiam? James, Joses, Judah le Simon-te sanggampa hi lel lo ahi hiam? A sanggam numeite zong i kiangah om uh hi lo ahi hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p Tua hi a, amaute in amah a sang zo kei uh hi.
\v 4 \x + \xo 6:4 \xt Luk 4:24; Joh 4:44\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Kamsang kici peuhmah ama khua, ama tanaute le ama innkuan sung simloh mundang khempeuh ah pahtawina ngah loin a om kei hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 5 Cina tawmkhatte tungah a khut nga in a damsak simloh, tua munah nalamdang bangmah a bawl thei kei hi.
\v 6 \x + \xo 6:6 \xt Mat 9:35; Luk 13:22\x*Amah in amaute up lohna uh lamdang a sa hi.
\s1 Sawm Le Nihte Kisawlkhia
\r Mat 10:1-42; Luk 9:1-6
\p Tua ciangin khuaneute ah zong a banbanin zin kawikawi in thu a hilh hi.
\v 7 \x + \xo 6:7 \xt Thu 17:6; Mat 10:1; Luk 10:1\x*Tua khit ciangin sawm le nihte ama kiangah sam a, nihta nihta in a sawlkhia hi. Dawigilote tungah thuneihna a pia hi.
\p
\v 8 Amah in amaute kiangah khualzinna ah a zat ding uh ciangkhut simloh thungip ahi a, an ahi a, sumbawm sungah sum ahi zongin bangmah a ken loh nading uh le
\v 9 khedap bulh in puanak a silh thuah loh nading uh thu a pia hi.
\v 10 Tua ciangin amaute kiangah, “Inn khatpeuh ah na tun uh ciangin tua khua pan na paikhiat matengun tua inn ah tamsuak un.
\v 11 \x + \xo 6:11 \xt Mat 10:14\x*Note hong sang nuam loin na thugen uh zong a ngai nuam lo mite khua pan na paikhiat uh ciangin note khenuai a leivuite singkhia un. Tua leivuite in amaute langkhat ah teci a suak ding hi. A man takpi kong cihin ah, thukhen ni ciangin Sodom le Gomorrah khua mite thuakna in tua khua mite thuakna sangin thuak nop zawlai ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 12 \x + \xo 6:12 \xt Luk 9:6\x*Tua ciangin a nungzuite paikhia uh a, mite a kisikkik nading thu a hilh uh hi.
\v 13 \x + \xo 6:13 \xt Jam 5:14\x*Dawi tampi hawlkhia in cina tampite sathau zutin a damsak uh hi.
\s1 Tuiphumpa John Kithat
\r Mat 14:1-14; Luk 9:7-9
\p
\v 14 \x + \xo 6:14 \xt Mat 3:1\x*Tu in, Zeisu minthang mahmah ahih manin Kumpipa Herod in ama thu a za hi. Tua ciangin amah in, “Tuiphumpa John misite lak pan hong thokik zo a, hih vangliatnate amah in a nei ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 15 \x + \xo 6:15 \xt Mal 4:5; Mat 16:14; 21:11\x*Mi pawlkhat in, “Hihpa Elijah ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. A dangte in, “Kamsangpa khat ahih keileh kamsangte khatpeuh tawh a kibang mi khat ahi hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 16 Ahih hangin Herod in a zak ciangin, “A ngawng ka tansa John mah misite lak pan hong thokik ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 17 \x + \xo 6:17 \xt Mat 4:12; Luk 3:19-20\x*Herod in a sanggampa Philip zi Herodias a teenpihna thu tawh kisai in John in Herod a mawhsak ngei hi. Tua ahih manin Herod in John mansak a, sikkhau tawh khih in thongah a khum hi.
\v 18 \x + \xo 6:18 \xt Siam 18:16\x*Banghang hiam cihleh John in Herod kiangah, “Na sanggampa zi na teenpih pen thukham tawh kituak lo hi,” ci in a gen manin tua banga a khum ahi hi.
\p
\v 19 Tua ahih manin Herodias in John mudah in a that nuam hi. Ahih hangin tua numei in a that thei kei hi.
\v 20 \x + \xo 6:20 \xt Mat 11:9\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Herod in John kihta a, John pen mi dik misiangtho ahihlam Herod in thei ahih manin amah a huu hi. John thugente in Herod lungsim buaisak mahmah a, ahih hangin a thugente hoih a sa mahmah hi.
\p
\v 21 \x + \xo 6:21 \xt Est 1:3; Luk 3:1\x*Tua ciangin Herod in ama suah ni in a uliante, a galkap mangte le Galilee gam miliante an a vak ciangin hun hoih khat a hong om hi.
\v 22 Tua ciangin Herodias tanu hong lutin hong lam a, Herod le amah tawh a tukhawm mite a lungkimsak mahmah hi.
\p Tua ciangin kumpipa in nungakno kiangah, “Na deih peuhpeuh hong ngen in kong pia ding hi.
\v 23 \x + \xo 6:23 \xt Est 5:3, 6\x*Ka gam phelkhat dongin nong nget peuhpeuh kong pia ding hi,” ci in kiciam in kamciam a pia hi.
\p
\v 24 Tua ciangin nungakno paikhia in a nu kiangah, “Bang ngen ding ka hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
\p A nu in, “Tuiphumpa John lutang va ngen in,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 25 Nungakno zong hong kilehkik pah vingveng in kumpipa kiangah, “Tuiphumpa John lutang kuangdai sung khat ah hong pia pah leteh ka ut hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 26 Kumpipa a dah mahmah hangin a kiciamna le ankuang a umpihte maitang zahtakna tawh nungakno ngetna a nial nuam kei hi.
\v 27 Tua ciangin kumpipa in mi thah nasep a sempa kiangah, “John lutang hong paipih in,” ci in thu a pia pah hi. Tua pa zong pai in thong sunga John ngawng va tan a,
\v 28 kuangdai sungkhat ah a lutang koihin tua nungakno pia a, nungakno in a nu a piasawn hi.
\v 29 John nungzuite in tua thu a zak uh ciangin pai in a luang la uh a, hanah a vui uh hi.
\s1 Mi 5,000 Anvakna
\r Mat 14:12-21; Luk 9:10-17; Joh 6:1-14
\p
\v 30 \x + \xo 6:30 \xt Mat 10:2; Luk 9:10; Saw 1:2, 26\x*Tua ciangin sawltakte Zeisu kiangah hong kituahkik uh a, a nasepte uh le a thuhilhna teng uh a gen uh hi.
\v 31 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Gamdaihna mun khat ah pai unla, tawmvei sung tawlnga un,” a ci hi.
\p Mi a ciah le a kuan kiphamat in annek hun ding nangawn ngah lo uh ahih manin tua banga a gen ahi hi.
\v 32 Tua ciangin amaute gunkuang khat tawh gamdaihna mun khat ah tuam paikhiat uh hi.
\v 33 Tu in amaute paikhiat mi honpi in mu uh a, mi tampi in Zeisu zong a kihel lam thei uh ahih manin khua khempeuh panin khe tawh hong tai ngeingai uh hi. Zeisu tun ma in tua mun na tungkhol uh a, Zeisu hong tun ciangin a kiangah hong kikhawm uh hi.
\v 34 \x + \xo 6:34 \xt Mat 9:36\x*Gunkuang sung pan Zeisu hong tuahkhiat ciangin mi honpite mu a, a cing om lo tuute tawh kibang uh ahih manin hehpihhuai sa in tua munah amaute thu tampi a hilh hi.
\p
\v 35 Nitum kuan ciangin nungzuite ama kiangah hong pai uh a, “Hih mun in gamlakpi hi a, ni zong tum dekta hi.
\v 36 Hih mite in annek ding bangmah nei lo uh ahih manin, an lei dingin hih kima om khuaneute ah paisak in,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 37 \x + \xo 6:37 \xt 2Ku 4:42-44\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Amaute nek theih khat peuhpeuh pia un,” a ci hi.
\p Nungzuite in, “Kote pai in \w denarius\w* 200 man an lei in a nek ding uh pia ding ka hi uh hiam?” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 38 \x + \xo 6:38 \xt Mat 15:34\x*Amah in, “Anlum bangzah nei na uh hiam? Pai unla va en dih un,” a ci hi.
\p Amaute in a omzah a theih khit uh ciangin, “Anlum nga le ngasa nih om hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 39 Tua ciangin Zeisu in mi khempeuh lopa tungah a honhon in tusak un ci in a sawl hi.
\v 40 Tua ciangin amaute pawlkhat 100, pawlkhat 50 ta in a pawlpawl in a tu uh hi.
\v 41 \x + \xo 6:41 \xt Mat 14:19\x*Zeisu in anlum nga le ngasa nihte a lak khit ciangin vantung lam ento in lungdam a ko hi. Tua khit ciangin anlumte balkham a, mite mai ah a lui dingin nungzuite a pia hi. Ngasa nihte zong mi khempeuh lakah a hawmsak hi.
\v 42 Tua ciangin mi khempeuh in gilvahtakin a ne uh hi.
\v 43 Anlum le ngasa kikhamval teng a kaihkhop uh ciangin lawh sawm le lawh nih dim a ngah uh hi.
\v 44 Anlum a ne mi pasal 5,000 bang a pha uh hi.
\s1 Zeisu Tui Tungah Lampai
\r Mat 14:22-33; Joh 6:15-21
\p
\v 45 \x + \xo 6:45 \xt Mat 11:21\x*Zeisu in mi honpi a ciahsak laitakin nungzuite gunkuang ah tuangsak mengmeng a, galkhat a om Bethsaida khua ah a mapaisak hi.
\v 46 \x + \xo 6:46 \xt Luk 3:21\x*Amaute a ciahkhiatsak khit ciangin thungen dingin mual tung ah a paito hi.
\p
\v 47 Tu in nitak hong tun ciangin tuili laizang ah gunkuang om a, tuili gei leitang tungah Zeisu bek a om hi.
\v 48 Tua ciangin huih lehnun ahih manin nungzuite in haksapi in gunkuang a hot uh Zeisu in a mu hi. Zanvil lina\f + \fr 6:48 \fk Zanvil lina\ft : Zingsang nai 3 pan nai 6 kikal hi.\f* hun pawlin amaute kiang zuanin Zeisu tui tungah hong pai a, amaute a kheng dektak hi.
\v 49 \x + \xo 6:49 \xt Luk 24:37\x*Amah tui tunga hong pai amaute in a muh uh ciangin, sikha sa in a kiko uh hi.
\v 50 \x + \xo 6:50 \xt Mat 14:27\x*Banghang hiam cihleh a vekpi un amah mu uh a, a patau uh hi.
\p Ahi zongin Zeisu in, “Lungnuam un! Keimah ka hi hi. Lau kei un,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 51 Tua ciangin amaute tuanna gunkuang ah Zeisu a kahtoh khit ciangin huih a dai hi. Amaute in gen zawh loh zahin lamdang a sa uh hi.
\v 52 Banghang hiam cihleh a lungtang uh khauhlua ahih manin anlum tawh nalamdang a bawlna thu a ngaihsun kha kei uh hi.
\p
\v 53 \x + \xo 6:53 \xt Joh 6:24-25\x*A galkhat ah a kah khit uh ciangin Gennesaret gam ah a pai uh a, tuili gei ah gunkuang a khih uh hi.
\v 54 Gunkuang sung pan a paikhiat uh ciangin mi khempeuh in Zeisu ahihlam thei pah uh a,
\v 55 amaute tua kima om gam tengah tai uh a, a cinate uh tal tawh hong pua in amah om hi ci a, a kizakna munmun ah a hong delh uh hi.
\v 56 \x + \xo 6:56 \xt Mat 9:20\x*Khuapi khuata le gam sung ama tunna peuhpeuh ah mite in kongzing lakah cinate sialin a puanmongtep beek a lawn khak theih nadingun a ngen tentan uh hi. Amah a lawng kha zahzah in damna a ngah uh hi.
\c 7 
\s1 A Siang Le A Siang Lo 
\r Mat 15:1-20 
\p 
\v 1 Tua khit ciangin Jerusalem khuapi pana hong pai Phariseete le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* pawlkhat Zeisu kiangah hong paikhawm uh hi. 
\v 2 \x + \xo 7:2 \xt Saw 10:14\x*Tu in a nungzuite kimkhat in khut ninsa a an a nek uh amaute in a muh uh ciangin a mawhsak uh hi. Khutnin a cih ciangin khutsil lo cihna ahi hi. 
\v 3 \x + \xo 7:3 \xt Luk 11:38\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Phariseete le Judah mi khempeuh in tanglai mite ngeina zui uh a, khutsil loin an ne lo uh hi. 
\v 4 \x + \xo 7:4 \xt Mat 23:25; Luk 11:39\x*Sumbuuk pan a ciah uh ciangin zong kisil loin an ne lo uh hi. Haite, belte, \w sumngo\w* kuangte le sabuaite sawpsiangna ngeina a kipan zuih ding a dang ngeina tampi zong neilai uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 7:5 \xt Gal 1:14; Col 2:8\x*Tua ciangin Pharisee pawlte le thukhamhilh siate in ama kiangah, “Na nungzuite in tanglai mite ngeina zui loin banghang in khutsil lopi in an ne uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Amah in amaute kiangah, “A kineihkhem note thu, kamsangpa Isaiah in \w Lai Siangtho\w* sunga a genkholhna thu a man hi. Amah in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Hih mite in a kam uh tawh a hong pahtawi uh hangin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt A lungsim uh kei tawh kigamla hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 7 \qt Mihing bawltawm thukhamte thuhilhna in zang uh ahih manin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Kei a hong biakna uh a mawkna ahi hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 7:7 \ft \+xt Isa 29:13\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 8 “Banghang hiam cihleh Pasian thupiakte nawlkhin in tanglai ngeina ahi bel le kuang sawpsiangna a kipan tua bang a dang ngeina tampi na zui uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 9 Amaute kiangah, “Tanglai ngeina na zuih theih nadingun Pasian thupiak na nawlkhin uh a, tua banga na hih uh ciangin hi na kisa mahmah uh hi. 
\v 10 Moses in, \qt ‘Na nu le na pa zahtak in,’\qt*\f + \fr 7:10 \ft \+xt Pai 20:12; Thu 5:16\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci a, \qt ‘A nu ahi a, a pa ahi zongin a samsia mi in thahna thuak tahen,’\qt*\f + \fr 7:10 \ft \+xt Pai 21:17; Siam 20:9\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in note thu hong pia hi. 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 7:11 \xt Mat 23:16, 18\x*“Ahih hangin, ‘Note in mi khat in a nu le a pa kiangah, “Kei tung pana na ngah ding khempeuh Corban\f + \fr 7:11 \fk Corban\ft : Greek kam hi in a khiatna pen “Pasian tunga kipia letsong” cihna hi.\f* hita hi,” ci peuh leh bangmah a piak kul nawn kei hi,’ na ci uh hi. Corban a khiatna in Pasian kipia khin cihna ahi hi. 
\v 12 Tua bang thu tawh a nu le a pa aa dingin tua pa in bangmah sep kul nawn lo hi na ci uh hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 7:13 \xt Heb 4:12\x*Note in na kihilh sawnsawn uh tanglai ngeinate zui in Pasian thu kimanna nei lo na suaksak uh a, tua bang dan ngeina tampi na nei uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 14 Amah in mi honpite a sap khit ciangin amaute kiangah, “Na vekpi un ka thugen ngai unla thei un. 
\v 15 A pualam panin mihing sunga tumsuk na khat beek in mi a ninsak thei kei hi. Mihing sung pana a pusuakkhiate bekin mihing a ninsak hi. 
\v 16 Zak nading bil a nei mi in za tahen!” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 17 Mi honpi lak pan amah paikhia a, inn sungah a lut khit ciangin a nungzuite in tua thugentehna thu a dong uh hi. 
\v 18 Tua ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “Note in zong tel lo na hi uh hiam? A pualam pan mihing sunga a tumsuk peuhmah in mi a ninsak thei kei hi. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 7:19 \xt Saw 10:15; Rom 14:1-12; Col 2:16; 1Ti 4:3-5\x*Banghang hiam cihleh lungsim sungah lut loin gilpi sungah lut a, a kine an khempeuh kithakhia in kisiangthosak hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Amah in, “Mihing sung pana pusuakte in tuami a ninsak hi. 
\v 21 Banghang hiam cihleh a sunglam a om mihingte lungsim panin ngaihsutna hoih lo, angkawmna, numei pasal mawhna, mi thahna, 
\v 22 \x + \xo 7:22 \xt Mat 20:15\x*guktakna, duhhopna, gitlohna, khemna, numei pasal paktatna, etsatna, kosiatna, kiphatsakna, haitatnate a hong pusuak hi. 
\v 23 Hih a hoih lo thute khempeuh sunglam pan hong pusuakin mihing a ninsak hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Syro-Phoenicia Numeinu Upna 
\r Mat 15:21-28 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 7:24 \xt Mat 11:21\x*Tua khit ciangin tua mun pan amah paikhia a, Tyre le Sidon gam sungah pai in inn khat ah a lut hi. Tualai ah a om lam kuama theih ding a ut loh hangin a kisel zo kei hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 7:25 \xt Mat 4:24\x*Dawigilo a vei tanu a nei nupi khat in Zeisu thu a zak ciangin hong pai a, Zeisu khephung ah bokin 
\v 26 a tanu sung pan dawi gilo a hawlkhiatsak nadingin a ngen den hi. Tua nu pen Syro-Phoenicia gama piang \w Greek\w* numei khat ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Ahih hangin Zeisu in tua nu kiangah, “Tate annek lai lakhia in uite piak ding kilawm lo hi. Tua ahih manin tate ka gilvahsak masa phot ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 28 Tua nu in, “Topa aw, hi mah hi. Ahi zongin sabuai nuai a om tate anneng kiate nangawn, uinote in ne kha sam uh hi lo ahi hiam?” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 29 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Tua banga na cih manin na tanu sung pan dawi gilo a taikhia zo hi. Ciahta in,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 30 Tua nu ama inn a tun ciangin lupna tungah a tanu lum a, ama sung pan dawi gilo paikhia khinzo cih a mu hi. 
\s1 Bengngong Le Pauthei Lo Damsakna 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 7:31 \xt Mat 11:21\x*Tyre le Sidon khua panin Zeisu paikhia leuleu a, \w Decapolis gam\w* kantan in Galilee tuili a tung hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 7:32 \xt Mat 9:32; Luk 11:14\x*Tua ciangin amaute in a bengngong, a pauthei lo mi khat ama kiangah hong paipih uh a, tua pa tungah a khut a ngak nadingin a ngen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 33 Zeisu in mi honpi lak panin tua pa paikhiatpih a, a bil langnih sungah a khutme guangin a cil phiha, a lei a lawnsak hi. 
\v 34 \x + \xo 7:34 \xt Joh 11:41\x*Tua khit ciangin vantung lam ento in khuisa a, ama kiangah, “Ephphatha,” a ci hi. A khiatna pen, “Kihong in,” a cihna ahi hi. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 7:35 \xt Isa 35:5-6\x*Tua pa thakhatin a bil kihong a, a leiigui zong kikhah in siangtakin a pau thei hi. 
\p 
\v 36 \x + \xo 7:36 \xt Mat 8:4\x*Tua ciangin tua thu kuama kiangah a gen loh nadingun Zeisu in thu a pia hi. Ahih hangin nak kham semsem le tua mite in a nak gen semsem uh hi. 
\v 37 Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Amah in na khempeuh a hoih in bawl a, bengngongte khuazasak in pau thei lote a pautheisak hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\c 8 
\s1 Mi 4,000 Anvakna 
\r Mat 15:32-39 
\p 
\v 1 Tua hun sungin mi honpite tamlua mahmah a, nek ding zong a nei kei uh hi. Tua ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite sam a, 
\v 2 \x + \xo 8:2 \xt Mat 9:36\x*“Hih mite ka kiangah ni thum hong om khin uh a, nek ding lah nei lo uh ahih manin hehpihhuai ka sa hi. 
\v 3 Gilkialsa in ciahsak leng amaute pawlkhat gamlapi pana hong pai uh ahih manin lamkal ah a bah ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Tua ciangin a nungzuite in, “Kua in mihing hi zahta hih gamlak ah an bangci vak zawh ding ahi hiam?” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Anlum bangzah nei na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. Amaute in, “Sagih a om hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Tua ciangin amah in mi honpite leilak ah tu dingin thu a piak khit ciangin anlum sagihte la in lungdam a ko hi. Tuate balnenin mipi lakah hawm dingin a nungzuite pia a, amaute in zong mi honpite lakah a hawm uh hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 8:7 \xt Mat 14:19\x*Amaute in ngasaneu tawmkha zong a nei uh hi. Amah in tuate thupha a piak khit ciangin mi honpite lakah hawm dingin thu a pia hi. 
\v 8 Tua ciangin amaute in a kham dong uh a nek khit uh ciangin a khamval uh a them a nengin kaikhawm uh a, lawhbeu sagih a ngah uh hi. 
\v 9 Tu in an a ne mi 4,000 bang a pha uh hi. Tua khit ciangin amah in amaute ciahsak in, 
\v 10 thakhat thu in nungzuite tawh gunkuang tung tuangin Dalmanutha gam ah a pai uh hi. 
\s1 Biakna Makaite In Limlamdang Ngen 
\r Mat 16:1-4 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 8:11 \xt Mat 12:38\x*Tua ciangin \w Pharisee\w* pawlte hong pai in Zeisu thugen nial dingin a kipan uh hi. Amah a ze-etna un, “Vantung panin limlamdang khat hong lak in,” ci in a ngen uh hi. 
\v 12 Ahih hangin a lungsim sungah Zeisu nakpi in khuisa a, “Banghang in tulai khang mite in nalamdang mu nuam uh ahi hiam? A man takpi kong cihin ah, tulai khang mite tungah limlamdang a kilak kei ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Amah in amaute nusia in gunkuang tuangkik a, galkhat lamah a paikhia hi. 
\s1 Pharisee Pawlte Le Herod Silngo 
\r Mat 16:5-12 
\p 
\v 14 Tu in a nungzuite in anlum puak ding mangngilh uh a, gunkuang sungah anlum khat longal a dang bangmah a nei kei uh hi. 
\v 15 \x + \xo 8:15 \xt Mat 14:1; Luk 12:1; 1Co 5:6-8\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Phariseete silngo le Herod silngo kidawm unla pelh un,” ci in thu a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Amaute in, “Anlum i neih loh manin hih banga hong ci ahi hi,” ci in a kikum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 8:17 \xt Isa 6:9-10\x*Tua banga thu a kikup uh Zeisu in a theih ciangin, “Anlum na neih loh manun banghang in tua bangin kikum na hi uh hiam? Phawk thei nai lo, tel thei nai lo na hi uh hiam? Na lungtang uh khauhsak lailai na hi uh hiam? 
\v 18 Mittang nei napi khuamu lo na hi uh hiam? Bil nei napi khuaza lo na hi uh hiam? Phawk thei mahmah lo na hi uh hiam? 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 8:19 \xt Mat 14:20; Luk 9:17; Joh 6:13\x*“Mi 5,000 aa dingin anlum nga ka balkhap ciangin a kikhamval an lawh bangzah ngah na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p Amaute in, “Lawh sawm le lawh nih,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 20 \x + \xo 8:20 \xt Mat 15:37\x*“Mi 4,000 aa dingin anlum sagih ka balkhap ciangin a kikhamval lawhbeu bangzah ngah na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p Amaute in, “Lawhbeu sagih,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 21 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Tua ahih leh bang dinga hih thu tel zo lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\s1 Mittaw Khat Kidamsak 
\p 
\v 22 \x + \xo 8:22 \xt Mat 11:21; Joh 9:1\x*Tua ciangin amah Bethsaida khua ah hong tung a, mite in ama kiangah mittaw khat hong paipihin tua pa a lawn nadingin a thum uh hi. 
\v 23 Tua ciangin amah in mittawpa a khut in kai a, khuanawl ah a paipih hi. Tua khit ciangin a mit cil phihsak in a tungah a khut a ngakh khit ciangin, “Na khatpeuh na mu thei ta hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 24 Tua pa khuadak in, “Mite ka et ciangin singkung lampai bangin ka mu hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 25 Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa mit tungah a khut khatvei nga kik a, tua khit ciangin a khuadaksak hi. A mit a ngei bangin hoihkik a, mi khempeuh teltakin a mu thei hi. 
\v 26 Tua ciangin amah in tua pa a inn ah ciahsak a, ama kiangah, “Khua sungah lut kei inla, hih thu kuama kiangah gen kei in,” ci in thu a pia hi. 
\s1 Peter In Khazih Pulak 
\r Mat 16:13-16; Luk 9:18-21 
\p 
\v 27 Tu in Zeisu le a nungzuite Caesarea Philippi gam khuaneute ah a pai uh hi. Lam a pai kawmun a nungzuite kiangah, “Mite in kei kua hi hong ci uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 28 \x + \xo 8:28 \xt Mal 4:5; Mat 3:1\x*Amaute in, “Mi pawlkhat in Tuiphumpa John hi hong ci uh hi. Pawlkhat in Elijah hi hong ci uh hi. Pawlkhat in kamsangte laka khat hi hong ci uh hi,” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 8:29 \xt Joh 6:69\x*Tua ciangin amah in, “Tua ahih leh note in kei kua hi nong ci uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p Peter in, “Nang in Khazih na hi hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 30 \x + \xo 8:30 \xt Mat 8:4; Luk 9:21\x*Tua ciangin amah in kuama kiangah ama thu a gen loh nadingun khauhtakin a kham hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih Ding Genkhol 
\r Mat 16:21-28; Luk 9:22-27 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 8:31 \xt Mat 8:20; 16:21; Saw 2:23\x*Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in, “\w Mihing Tapa\w* in gimna tampi thuak ding a, makaite, siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in nialin a that ding uh hi. Ni thum khit ciangin a thokik ding hi,” ci in a nungzuite a hilhta hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 8:32 \xt Joh 18:20\x*Amah in hih thu siangtakin a gen ciangin Peter in amah samkhia in a taii hi. 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 8:33 \xt Mat 4:10\x*Ahih hangin amah kihei in a nungzuite en kawmsa in Peter lehtaii a, “\w Satan\w* aw, ka nunglam ah kihemkhia in. Pasian nate ngaihsun loin mihing nate na ngaihsun hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 8:34 \xt Mat 10:38; Luk 14:27\x*Tua ciangin amah in mi honpite le a nungzuite samkhawm a, amaute kiangah, “Kei hong zui nuam mi peuhmah in ama pumpi deihna nial henla, a singlamteh pua in ka nung hong zui hen. 
\v 35 \x + \xo 8:35 \xt Joh 12:25\x*Banghang hiam cihleh ama nuntakna a huu nuam mi in a nuntakna a tan ding hi. Keimah le lungdamna thu hanga a nuntakna a tan mi in a nuntakna a honkhia ahi ding hi. 
\v 36 Banghang hiam cihleh mi khat in leitung buppi a ngah hangin ama nuntakna a suplawh leh bang phattuamna om ding ahi hiam? 
\v 37 Ahih keileh ama nuntakna bang tawh khekkik thei ding ahi hiam? 
\v 38 \x + \xo 8:38 \xt Mat 8:20; Luk 12:9; 1Th 2:19\x*Angkawm hat le mawhna a bawl tulai khang mite lakah kei le ka thu a maizumpih mi peuhmah Mihing Tapa in ama Pa minthanna silh a, a siangtho vantungmite tawh a hong pai ciangin a maizumpih ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 9 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 9:1 \xt Mat 24:30; Luk 22:18\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, hih laitak a a ding mi pawlkhat in vangliatna tawh a hong tung Pasian kumpigam a muh matengun sihna a ciam kha kei ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Mel Kikhelna 
\r Mat 17:1-13; Luk 9:28-36 
\p 
\v 2 \x + \xo 9:2 \xt Mat 4:21\x*Tu in ni guk khit ciangin Zeisu in Peter, James le Johnte a tuamin samkhia a, mual sang tung khat ah a kahtohpih hi. Tua khit ciangin amaute mai ah a mel a kikhel hi. 
\v 3 \x + \xo 9:3 \xt Mat 28:3\x*A puante tee deldel a, vuk bangin a pak sitset hi. Leitung a puansawpmi kuama peuh in tua zahin a paksak zo kei ding hi. 
\v 4 Tua ciangin Elijah le Moses hong kilang uh a, Zeisu tawh a kiho uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 9:5 \xt Mat 23:7\x*Tua ciangin Peter in Zeisu kiangah, “\w Rabbi\w* aw, hihlai nuam ka sa uh hi. Nang aa ding buuk khat, Moses aa ding buuk khat, Elijah aa ding buuk khat, buuk thum kong lamsak ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Amaute lau mahmah uh a, gen ding mel a theih loh man ahi hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 9:7 \xt Pai 24:16; Mat 3:17\x*Tua laitakin meiilom khat in amaute tuam a, tua meii sung panin, “Hihpa in ka it ka Tapa ahi hi. Ama thu na mang un!” ci in aw khat hong gingkhia hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Amaute in a kim a pam envat uh a, Zeisu longal kuamah dang a mu nawn kei uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 9:9 \xt Mat 8:20\x*Tu in mual tung pan amaute hong kumsuk uh a, \w Mihing Tapa\w* misite lak pan a thawhkik khit matengin hih a muh uh nate kuama kiangah a gen loh nadingun thu a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Tua hi a, misite lak panin thokik a cih in bang a cihnopna ahi tam ci in kidong uh a, tua thu amau teng theih bekin a ciamteh uh hi. 
\v 11 Amaute in, “Banghang in \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in Elijah hong pai masa ding hi ci uh ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 9:12 \xt Mat 8:20; Luk 23:11\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Elijah hong pai masa in na khempeuh a ngeina bangsakkik ding hi. Tua ahih leh banghang in Mihing Tapa in zong gimna tampi thuak ding a, mite simmawh in om ding hi ci in kigelh ahi hiam? 
\v 13 \x + \xo 9:13 \xt Mat 11:14\x*Ahi zongin ken kong cih in ah Elijah hong pai khinzo a, ama thu a kigelhsa bangin amaute in a utut un a bawl khinzo uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Dawilut Pasalno Kidamsak 
\r Mat 17:14-21; Luk 9:37-43 
\p 
\v 14 A nungzuite kiangah Zeisu hong pai ciangin amaute kimkot a om mi honpi a mu hi. Thukhamhilh siate zong amaute tawh thu kisel in na om uh hi. 
\v 15 Amaute khempeuh in Zeisu a muhvat uh ciangin lamdangsa mahmah uh a, ama kiangah tai in a hopih uh hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Amah in thukhamhilh siate kiangah, “Amaute tawh bang thu kikum na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 17 Tua ciangin mi honpi lak pan mi khat in, “Sia aw, ka tapa sungah dawi lutin pau thei lo ahih manin nang kiangah kong paipih uh hi. 
\v 18 Tua dawi in amah a mat ciangin a matna mun peuhpeuh ah leitang a denna hi. Tua ciangin a cilphuan kai in a ha gawi a, a kongkawgawp hi. Tua hi a, hih dawi hong hawlkhiatsak dingin na nungzuite kiangah ka nget hangin a hawlkhia zo kei uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 19 Zeisu in, “Upna a nei lo khang mite aw, bang tanvei hong ompih a, bang tanvei hong thuak lai ding ka hi hiam? Tua naupang ka kiangah hong paipih un,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 20 Tua ciangin amaute in Zeisu kiangah tua pa hong paipih uh hi. Zeisu a muh ciangin dawi in tua pa thakhatin a kongkawsak hi. Tua khit ciangin lei ah tua pa pukin kipek a, a kam panin cilphuan a kai hi. 
\p 
\v 21 Zeisu in tua pasalno ii pa kiangah, “Ahi cih zawh bang tanvei sawt zo ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p A pa in, “A neutung a kipan ahi hi. 
\v 22 A sih nadingin tua dawi in tamveipi mei sungah puksak in tui sungah a kiasak hi. Ahi zongin nong hihsak theih a om leh hong hehpih inla hong huh in,” ci in a ngen hi. 
\p 
\v 23 \x + \xo 9:23 \xt Mat 21:21; Joh 11:40\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Na up nak leh a um mite aa dingin na khempeuh a piang thei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 24 Tua ciangin pasalno ii a pa kikokhia pah a, “Topa aw, ka um hi. Ka up lohna hong huh in!” ci in khitui luangin a ngen hi. 
\p 
\v 25 Zeisu in mi honpite ama lamah hong tai a muh ciangin tua dawigilo kiangah, “Nang a pau thei lo le a bengngong dawi aw, ama sung panin taikhia a, na lutkik nawh loh nadingin thu kong pia hi,” ci in a taii hi. 
\p 
\v 26 Tua ciangin tua dawi kikokhia in, pasalno nakpitak kongkawsak a, tua khit ciangin ama sung panin a paikhia hi. Tua pa misi tawh kibang ahih manin mi tampi in, “Amah si ta hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 27 Ahih hangin Zeisu in ama khut lenin a phot ciangin a thoto hi. 
\v 28 Inn sungah Zeisu a lut khit ciangin nungzuite in, “Kote in banghang in tua dawi hawlkhia zo lo ka hi uh hiam?” ci in a dongsim uh hi. 
\p 
\v 29 Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Hih bang dawi namte thungetna le antanna lo tawh paikhia lo hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih ding Nihvei A Genkholhna 
\r Mat 17:22-23; Luk 9:43-45 
\p 
\v 30 Tua ciangin amaute tua mun pan paikhia in Galilee gam kantan uh a, Zeisu in tua thu kuama theih ding a deih kei hi. 
\v 31 \x + \xo 9:31 \xt Mat 8:20; Saw 2:23\x*Banghang hiam cihleh amah in a nungzuite kiangah, “Mite khut ah Mihing Tapa kilehhek ding a, kithat ding hi. A kithah zawh ni thum khit ciangin a thokik ding hi,” ci in a hilh hi. 
\p 
\v 32 \x + \xo 9:32 \xt Luk 2:50; Joh 12:16\x*Ahih hangin amaute in a thugen tel lo uh a, zong a dong ngam tuan kei uh hi. 
\s1 Kua Lianpen 
\r Mat 18:1-9; Luk 9:46-50 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 9:33 \xt Mat 4:13\x*Tua ciangin amaute Capernaum khua hong tung uh a, inn sung khat ah a om laitakun amah in, “Lamkal ah bang thu kisel na hi uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 9:34 \xt Luk 22:24\x*Amaute lakah kua lianpen ding hiam cih thu lamkal ah kisel uh ahih manin pau loin a omtek uh hi. 
\p 
\v 35 \x + \xo 9:35 \xt Mat 18:4; Luk 22:26\x*Tua ciangin amah tusukin nungzui sawm le nihte sam a, amaute kiangah, “Mi khatpeuh a masa pen ding a ut leh a nunung pen hi ding a, mi khempeuh nasempa zong hi ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 36 Tua khit ciangin naupangno khat samin amaute laizang ah a koih khit ciangin a ang ah tawi a, 
\v 37 \x + \xo 9:37 \xt Mat 10:40\x*“Hih bang naupangno khat keima minin a sang mi in kei hong sang ahi hi. Kei hong sang mi in kei hong sang hi loin kei hong sawlpa a sang ahi hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Hong Langpan Lote I Pawl 
\r Luk 9:49, 50 
\p 
\v 38 \x + \xo 9:38 \xt Gam 11:27-29\x*Tu in John in, “Sia aw, eite hong zui lo mi khat in nangma min tawh dawite a hawlkhiat ka mu uh hi. Amah in eite hong zui lo ahih manin ka kham uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 39 Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “Tua pa kham kei un. Keima min tawh nalamdang a bawl mi in kei hong gensia lo pah ding hi. 
\v 40 \x + \xo 9:40 \xt Mat 12:30; Luk 11:23\x*Banghang hiam cihleh ei hong langpan lo peuhpeuh ei lam a pang hi pah uh hi. 
\v 41 \x + \xo 9:41 \xt Mat 10:42\x*A man takpi kong cihin ah, Khazih mi na hih manun kei mina note tui hai khat a hong suah mi peuhmah in thaman ngah loin a om kei ding hi. 
\s1 Midangte Puksakna 
\r Mat 18:6-9 
\p 
\v 42 \x + \xo 9:42 \xt Mat 5:29; Luk 17:2\x*“Kei hong um hih naupangnote khat a puksak mi peuhmah a ngawng ah angawina suang khih henla tuipi sungah kikhia leh ama aa dingin a hoihzaw ding hi. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 9:43 \xt Mat 5:29\x*Na khut in hong khialh sak leh sattan in. Khut nih nei in \w hell\w* le a mit ngei lo meikuang sungah na lut sangin khuttawngsa in nuntakna munah lut leteh nang aa dingin a hoihzaw ding hi. 
\b 
\q1 
\v 44 \qt ‘Tua hell sungah a thante uh si thei loin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Meikuang zong a mit ngei kei hi.’\qt*\f + \fr 9:44 \ft \+xt Isa 66:24\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\b 
\p 
\v 45 \x + \xo 9:45 \xt Mat 5:29\x*“Na khe in hong khialh sak leh sattan in. Khe nih nei a hell le a mit ngei lo meikuang sungah hong kipaih sangin khetawng sa in nuntakna munah lut leteh nang aa dingin hoihzaw ding hi. 
\b 
\q1 
\v 46 \qt ‘Tua hell sungah a thante uh si thei loin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Meikuang zong a mit ngei kei hi.’\qt* 
\b 
\p 
\v 47 \x + \xo 9:47 \xt Mat 5:29\x*“Na mit in hong khialh sak leh khelkhia in. Mittang nih nei in hell meikuang sungah hong kikhiat sangin mittang khat guak tawh Pasian kumpigam sungah lut leteh nang aa dingin hoihzaw ding hi. 
\b 
\q1 
\v 48 \x + \xo 9:48 \xt Mat 25:41\x*\qt ‘Tua hell sungah a thante uh si thei loin,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Meikuang zong a mit ngei kei hi.’\qt* 
\b 
\p 
\v 49 \x + \xo 9:49 \xt Siam 2:13\x*“Banghang hiam cihleh biakpiakna a kigosa khempeuh ci a kisawh bangin mi khempeuh zong mei tawh kihahsiang ding hi. 
\v 50 \x + \xo 9:50 \xt Mat 5:13; Luk 14:34-35; Rom 12:18; 2Co 13:11; Col 4:6; 1Th 5:13\x*Ahih hangin ci pen al nawn keileh bangci bangin ki-alkiksak thei ding ahi hiam? Ci bangin al ciat unla, khat le khat kilem in om un,” a ci hi. 
\c 10
\s1 Nupa Kimakna
\r Mat 5:31, 32; 19:3-10
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 10:1 \xt Mat 4:23; Joh 10:40\x*Tua ciangin tua mun panin Zeisu dingkhia a, Jordan Gun gal Judea gam a tung hi. Tua ciangin ama kiangah mi honpite hong kikhawmkik uh a, a hih ngei bangin amaute thu a hilhkik hi.
\p
\v 2 \w Pharisee\w* pawlte ama kiangah hong pai uh a, “Mi khat in a zi a mak ding thukham tawh a kituak hiam?” ci in ze-et in a dong uh hi.
\v 3 Amah in amaute dawngkik a, “Moses in note bang thu hong pia ahi hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 4 \x + \xo 10:4 \xt Thu 24:1-4; Mat 5:31\x*Amaute in, “Kimakna lai gelh in a zi mak theih nading thu Moses in hong pia hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 5 \x + \xo 10:5 \xt Lat 95:8; Heb 3:15\x*Zeisu in dawng a, “Na lungtang uh khauhlua ahih manin Moses in hih thupiak a gelh ahi hi.
\v 6 \x + \xo 10:6 \xt Pian 5:2\x*Ahih hangin lei a piansak cil in, \qt Pasian in pasal le numei a bawl hi.\qt*\f + \fr 10:6 \ft \+xt Pian 1:27; 5:2\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\v 7 \qt Tua ahih manin pasal in a nu le a pa nusia in a zi tawh kigawm ding a,\qt*
\v 8 \x + \xo 10:8 \xt 1Co 6:16\x*\qt Amaute gel pumkhat a suak ding uh hi.\qt*\f + \fr 10:8 \ft \+xt Pian 2:24\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* Tua hi a, amaute nih hi nawn loin pumkhat ahi uh hi.
\v 9 Tua ahih manin Pasian in a gawmsate mihing in khen kei tahen,” ci in a dawng hi.
\p
\v 10 A nungzuite in zong inn sungah hih thu mah a dongkik uh hi.
\v 11 \x + \xo 10:11 \xt Luk 16:18\x*Tua ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “A zi ma a, numei dang tawh a kiteeng peuhmah in a zi a angkawmsan ahi hi.
\v 12 \x + \xo 10:12 \xt Rom 7:3; 1Co 7:10-11\x*Numei in zong a pasal ciahsan a, pasal dang tawh a kiteen leh angkawm mah ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Naupangnote Thupha Pia
\r Mat 19:13-15; Luk 18:15-17
\p
\v 13 Tua khit ciangin Zeisu lawn dingin naupangnote ama kiangah hong paipih uh hi. Ahi zongin a nungzuite in tua mite na taiigawp uh hi.
\v 14 \x + \xo 10:14 \xt Mat 25:34\x*Zeisu in a muh ciangin lungkim lo a amaute kiangah, “Naupangnote ka kiangah hong paisak unla kham kei un. Pasian kumpigam in naupangno tawh a kibangte aa ahi hi.
\v 15 \x + \xo 10:15 \xt Mat 18:3\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, naupangnote san banga Pasian kumpigam a sang lo mi peuhmah tua kumpigam sungah a lut thei kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 16 Tua khit ciangin naupangnote a ang ah tawi in amaute tungah a khut nga in thupha a pia hi.
\s1 A Hau Tangvalpa In Thu Dong
\r Mat 19:16-30; Luk 18:18-30
\p
\v 17 \x + \xo 10:17 \xt Luk 10:25; Saw 20:32\x*Amah lampi ah a pai laitakin mi khat hong tai in ama mai ah a khukdin khit ciangin, “Sia hoih aw, nuntak tawntungna ka luah nadingin bang hih ding ka hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
\p
\v 18 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Banghang in mi hoih hong ci na hi hiam? Pasian khatbek longal a hoih kuamah om lo hi.
\v 19 \qt ‘Angkawm kei in. Mi that kei in. Gu kei in. A man loin teci pang kei in.\f + \fr 10:19 \ft \+xt Pai 20:13-16; Thu 5:17-20\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* Thuman lopi in mi van laksak kei in.\f + \fr 10:19 \ft \+xt Thu 24:14\+xt*\qt pana kila ahi hi.\qt*\f* Na nu le na pa zahtak in,’\qt*\f + \fr 10:19 \ft \+xt Pai 20:12; Thu 5:16\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* cih thukhamte na thei hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 20 Tua ciangin tua pa in, “Sia aw, tuate khempeuh ka neutunga kipan ka zuih khitsa ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 21 \x + \xo 10:21 \xt Mat 6:20; Luk 12:33; Saw 2:45\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in tua pa en a, it ahih manin, “Na kisap khat om hi. Pai in na neihsa teng zuak inla, mi zawngte pia in. Tua hi leh vantung ah sum na nei ding hi. Tua khit ciangin hong pai inla, singlamteh pua in hong zui in,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 22 Tua pa hau mahmah ahih manin hih thu hangin dah a, maikhingsa in a paikhia hi.
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 10:23 \xt Lat 52:7; 1Ti 6:9-10, 17\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in a kim a pam en a, a nungzuite kiangah, “Mi haute Pasian kumpigam sungah a lut ding uh haksa mahmah hi!” a ci hi.
\p
\v 24 \x + \xo 10:24 \xt Mat 7:13-14; Joh 3:5\x*A nungzuite in ama thugen lamdangsa mahmah uh a, ahih hangin Zeisu in, “Tate aw, hauhna suanga Pasian kumpigam sung lut a sawmte aa dingin nak haksat zen si in cia!
\v 25 \x + \xo 10:25 \xt Luk 12:16-20\x*Mi hau khat Pasian kumpigam sung a lut ding sangin kalaoh khat phimbilvang a khum ding baih zaw hi!” a ci hi.
\p
\v 26 Amaute in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, “Tua bang ahih leh kua in hotkhiatna ngah zo ding ahi hiam?” a kici uh hi.
\p
\v 27 \x + \xo 10:27 \xt Mat 19:26\x*Zeisu in amaute en in a genin ah, “Hih thu mihing tawh a pian theih loh hangin Pasian tawh tua bang ahi kei hi; banghang hiam cihleh Pasian tawh na khempeuh a piang thei hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 28 \x + \xo 10:28 \xt Mat 4:19\x*Tua ciangin Peter in, “En in, kote in na khempeuh uh nusia in nang kong zui uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 29 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, mi khatpeuh in keima hang leh lungdamna thu hangin a inn a lo, a sanggampa a sanggamnu, a nu a pa, a zi a tate, khat peuhpeuh a nusiat leh,
\v 30 \x + \xo 10:30 \xt Mat 6:33\x*tuami in tuhun mahin innte, sanggam pasal le sanggam numei, nute, tate le lote a zah 100 a ngah ding hi. Amah in bawlsiatna zong thuak ding a, hong tung ding hun ah nuntak tawntungna a ngah ding hi.
\v 31 \x + \xo 10:31 \xt Mat 19:30\x*Ahih hangin a masa mi tampite nunung ding uh a, a nunung mi tampite masa ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu In A Sih Ding Genkholkik
\r Mat 20:17-19; Luk 18:31-34
\p
\v 32 Tu in Jerusalem khuapi ah paito uh a, amaute mai ah Zeisu a pai hi. Nungzuite in lamdangsa mahmah uh a, amah a zui midangte a lau uh hi. Amah in sawm le nihte samkhiakik in ama tunga thupiang dingte a gen in ah,
\v 33 \x + \xo 10:33 \xt Luk 9:51\x*“En un, Jerusalem khuapi ah i paito ding hi. Siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* tungah \w Mihing Tapa\w* kilehhek ding a, amaute in thah dingin thu khenin Gentilete khut ah a piakhia ding uh hi.
\v 34 \x + \xo 10:34 \xt Mat 16:21; Saw 2:23\x*Amaute in amah zahko in, sat in, cilphih in that ding uh a, ni thum khit ciangin a thokik ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 James Le John-te Ngetna
\r Mat 20:20-28
\p
\v 35 Tua ciangin Zebedee tapate James le John hong pai uh a, ama kiangah, “Sia aw, kong nget peuhpeuh uh hong hihsak lecin ka ut uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 36 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Note aa dingin bang hong hihsak leng ut na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 37 \x + \xo 10:37 \xt Mat 19:28\x*Amaute in ama kiangah, “Na minthanna ah na tut ciangin na taklam ah khat, na veilam ah khat hong tusak in,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 38 \x + \xo 10:38 \xt Job 38:2; Mat 20:22; Luk 12:50\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Nong nget uh bang thu hiam cih na thei kei uh hi. Ka dawn ding hai dawn zo ding na hi uh hiam, ka kibaptize nading ah kibaptize zo ding na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 39 \x + \xo 10:39 \xt Saw 12:2; Kil 1:9\x*Amaute in, “Ka hih zo ding uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Ka dawn ding hai na dawn takpi ding uh a, ka kibaptize nading ah zong na kibaptize takpi ding uh hi.
\v 40 Ahih hangin ka taklam le ka veilam a tut ding pen kei hong piak theih hi lo hi. A ngah ding a kisehkholsa mite aa ding ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 41 Tua thu a dang sawmte in a zak uh ciangin James le Johnte tungah a lungkim kei uh hi.
\v 42 Ahih hangin Zeisu in amaute ama kiangah sam a, “Gentilete sungah a uk dinga a kiseh mite in amaute ukcip uh a, a miliante un zong mipite tungah thuneihna a zang uh hi cih na thei uh hi.
\v 43 Ahih hangin note lakah tua bang ding hi lo hi. Note lakah a lian a suak nuam peuhmah in note nasem ahi ding hi.
\v 44 Note lakah a masa pen a suak nuam mi peuhmah mi khempeuh sila ahi ding hi.
\v 45 \x + \xo 10:45 \xt Mat 20:28\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Mihing Tapa nangawn ama na a kisepsak dinga hong pai hi lo hi. Midangte na a sepsak ding le a nuntakna pia in mi tampi a tankhia dinga hong pai ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Bartimaeus In Khuamu
\r Mat 20:29-34; Luk 18:35-43
\p
\v 46 Tu in amaute Jericho khua hong tung uh hi. Zeisu le a nungzuite mi hon tampite tawh tonin Jericho khua pan a paikhiat laitakun Timaeus tapa Bartimaeus kici mittaw khat khutdawhngen in lam gei ah na tu hi.
\v 47 \x + \xo 10:47 \xt Mat 9:27\x*Amah in Nazareth mi Zeisu hi cih a zak ciangin, “David Tapa, Zeisu aw, kei hong hehpih in!” ci in a kiko hi.
\p
\v 48 Tua ciangin mi tampite in a daih nadingin a kham uh hangin amah kinak ko semsem a, “David Tapa aw, kei hong hehpih in!” a ci hi.
\p
\v 49 Tua ciangin Zeisu dinkhawl a, “Amah sam un,” ci in thu a pia hi. Amaute in mittawpa kiangah, “Lungnuam inla dingto in. Amah in nang hong sam hi,” a ci uh hi.
\v 50 Mittawpa in a puan lawnkhia in dingto a, Zeisu kiangah a pai hi.
\p
\v 51 \x + \xo 10:51 \xt Mat 23:7\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Nang aa dingin bang hong hihsak leng ut na hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
\p Mittawpa in, “\w Rabboni\w*\f + \fr 10:51 \fk Rabboni\ft : Aramaic pau hi in “Ka Siapa” ahih keileh “Ka Mangpa” cihna hi a, ki-it kinaina a lak deuh kammal hi.\f* aw, khua mu thei leng ka ut hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 52 \x + \xo 10:52 \xt Mat 9:22\x*Zeisu in ama kiangah, “Ciah in, na upna in nang hong damsak zo hi,” a ci hi.
\p Amah in thakhatin khuamu pah a, lamdung ah Zeisu a zui hi.
\c 11 
\s1 Jerusalem Ah Gual Zo A Lutna 
\r Mat 21:1-11; Luk 19:28-40; Joh 12:12-19 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 11:1 \xt Mat 21:17\x*Amaute in Jerusalem khuapi tun kuan, Olive Mual kianga om Bethphage le Bethany khua a tun uh ciangin Zeisu in a nungzuite nih sawl a, 
\v 2 \x + \xo 11:2 \xt Gam 19:2; Thu 21:3; 1Sa 6:7\x*“Note mai a om khua ah va pai un. Khuasung na lut phetun kuama tuan ngei nai loh laano khat kikhih a om na mu ding uh hi. Suut unla hong kai un. 
\v 3 Mi khatpeuh in, ‘Banghang in suut na hi uh hiam?’ hong cih leh, ‘Topa in deih hi,’ amah in hihlai ah hong puak pah ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Amaute pai uh a, kongzing a inn pualam kongkhak gei ah a kikhih laano mu in a suut uh hi. 
\v 5 Tualai a a ding mi pawlkhat in, “Banghang in tua laano suut na hi uh hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Amaute in Zeisu thupiakna bangin a gen uh ciangin tua mite in a paisak uh hi. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 11:7 \xt Zec 9:9\x*Tua ciangin amaute in tua laano Zeisu kiangah hong paipih uh a, a tungah a puante uh a phah khit uh ciangin Zeisu a tuang hi. 
\v 8 Mi tampite in lampi ah a puante uh phah a, a dangte in nisuh hiangte khiak in a phah uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 11:9 \xt Mat 23:39\x*Ama mai a paite le a nung a zui mite kiko in a gen in ah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt “\+w Hosanna\+w*!\qt* 
\q1 \qt Topa min tawh hong paipa in, Thupha ngah tahen!\qt*\f + \fr 11:9 \ft \+xt Lat 118:25-26\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\q1 
\v 10 \x + \xo 11:10 \xt Luk 2:14\x*Topa minin a hong tung ding, 
\q1 I pa David kumpigam in thupha ngah tahen! 
\q1 A sangbel munah Hosanna!” 
\m a ci uh hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 11 \x + \xo 11:11 \xt Mat 21:12, 17\x*Tua khit ciangin Jerusalem \w biakinnpi\w* huang sungah Zeisu lutin na khempeuh a en kawikawi hi. Ni hong tumkuan ta ahih manin sawm le nihte tawh Bethany khua ah a ciahkik uh hi. 
\s1 Theikung Hamsiatna 
\r Mat 21:18, 19 
\p 
\v 12 A zingciang in amaute Bethany khua pan paikhia uh a, Zeisu a gil a kial hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 11:13 \xt Luk 13:6-9\x*Gamlapi a om a teh a nei thei kung khat a muh ciangin a gah hiam cih en dingin a va zuan hi. Theikung kianga tun ciangin thei min hun hi lo ahih manin a teh longal bangmah mu lo hi. 
\v 14 Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Tu a kipan kuamah in na gah ne nawn kei tahen,” a ci hi. Tua bang a cih a nungzuite in a za uh hi. 
\s1 Biakinnpi Siansuahna 
\r Mat 21:12, 13; Luk 19:45-48 
\p 
\v 15 Amaute Jerusalem khuapi hong tun uh ciangin biakinnpi huang sungah Zeisu a lut hi. Biakinnpi huang sungah van lei van zuak a om mite hawlkhia a, \w sumkhekte\w* sabuaite le vakhu zuakte tutphahte a lumletsak hi. 
\v 16 Biakinnpi huang sungah kuamah in van zuak ding khat peuhpeuh a puak loh nadingin zong a kham hi. 
\v 17 Tua khit ciangin hih bangin amaute thu hilh a, “\w Lai Siangtho\w* sungah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Ka inn in minamte khempeuh thungetna inn kici ding hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 11:17 \ft \+xt Isa 56:7\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in kigelh hi lo ahi hiam? 
\b 
\m Ahih hangin note in \qt ‘gutate phualpi,’\qt*\f + \fr 11:17 \ft \+xt Jer 7:11\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* na suaksak uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 11:18 \xt Mat 21:46; Luk 20:19\x*\w Thukhamhilh siate\w* le siampi liante in tua thu a zak uh ciangin amah thah theih nading lampi a zong uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh mi khempeuh in ama thuhilhna lamdangsa mahmah uh ahih manin amaute in amah kihta uh hi. 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 11:19 \xt Luk 21:37\x*Nitak lam ciangin khuapi sung pan Zeisu a paikhia hi. 
\s1 Theikung Keugaw 
\r Mat 21:20-22 
\p 
\v 20 A zingciang in amaute in thei kung omna gei hong tung uh a, tua thei kung a zung a kipan keugawcip in a om a mu uh hi. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 11:21 \xt Mat 23:7\x*Peter in Zeisu kammal phawkkik a, “\w Rabbi\w* aw, en dih ve! Na samsiat thei kung a keugaw hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 22 Zeisu in dawngkik in amaute kiangah, “Pasian um un. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 11:23 \xt Mat 21:21\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, mi khatpeuh in hih mualpi kiangah, ‘Kikhinkhia inla tuipi sung kidenna in,’ ci in thupia in, ka cih bangin piang ding hi ci in lunghiang loin a up takpi leh a cih bangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 24 \x + \xo 11:24 \xt Mat 7:7\x*Tua ahih manin ken kong cih in ah thu na nget uh ciangin ka nget khempeuh ka ngah hi ci in na up uh leh na ngah ding uh hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 11:25 \xt Mat 6:14\x*Thu na nget uh ciangin mi dang khat peuhpeuh tungah lungkim lohna na neih uh leh maisak masa un. Tua hi leh vantung a om na Pa un note mawhna zong hong maisak ding hi. 
\v 26 Ahih hangin na maisak kei uh leh vantung a om na Pa un note mawhna zong hong maisak lo ding hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Thuneihna Kidong 
\r Mat 21:23-27; Luk 20:1-8 
\p 
\v 27 Tua ciangin amaute Jerusalem khuapi ah hong paikik uh hi. Biakinnpi huang sungah Zeisu a vak kawikawi laitakin siampi liante, thukhamhilh siate le makaite ama kiangah a hong pai uh hi. 
\v 28 Amaute in ama kiangah, “Bang thuneihna tawh hih nate sem na hi hiam? Hih nate na sep nadingin thuneihna kua in hong pia ahi hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi. 
\p 
\v 29 Zeisu in amaute dawng a, “Ken zong thu khat kong dong ding hi. Tua ciangin hong dawng un. Nong dawn theih uh leh bang thuneihna tawh hih nate sem ka hi hiam cih kong gen ding hi. 
\v 30 John tuiphumna thu, vantung pan ahi hiam ahih keileh mihing tung pan ahi hiam? Hong dawng dih un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 31 Tua ciangin amaute kikum uh a, “~‘Vantung pana hong pai hi,’ ci lehang, ‘Banghang in amah um lo na hi uh hiam?’ hong ci ding hi. 
\v 32 \x + \xo 11:32 \xt Mat 11:9\x*‘Mihing tung pana hong pai hi,’ ci lehang lah mite khempeuh in John pen kamsang taktak a a san uh ahih manin mite i kihta hi,” a kici uh hi. 
\p 
\v 33 Tua ahih manin, “Ka thei kei uh hi,” ci in a dawng uh hi. 
\p Zeisu in, “Ken zong bang thuneihna tawh hih nate sem ka hi hiam cih kong gen kei ding hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\c 12 
\s1 Lenggahhuan Le A Khote Thugentehna 
\r Mat 21:33-46; Luk 20:9-18 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 12:1 \xt Isa 5:1-7\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah thugentehna tawh thugen kipan a, “Mi khat in lenggahhuan khat bawl a, suang tawh dai umin lenggah cil nading mun le tausang khat zong a dawh hi. Tua khit ciangin lokhawh thalawhte khosak in khual gamlapi khat ah a zinsan hi. 
\v 2 Lenggah lak hun ciangin lokhawh thalawhte kiangah a gah pawlkhat la dingin a nasemte khat a paisak hi. 
\v 3 Amaute in tua pa manin a vuak khit uh ciangin khutguakin a ciahsak uh hi. 
\v 4 Tua ciangin huan neipa in a dang nasem khat a sawlkik hi. Amaute in tua pa suang tawh dengin a lutang satliam uh a, a zumhuaipi in bawlin a ciahsak uh hi. 
\v 5 Huan neipa in nasem dang khat sawlkik leuleu a, amaute in tua pa a that uh hi. Nasem dang tampi sawlbeh a, tuate zong pawlkhat vua in, pawlkhat a that uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 \x + \xo 12:6 \xt Heb 1:1-3\x*“Tu in huan neipa in a sawl theih ding a it mahmah a tapa khat bek omlai ahih manin amah in, ‘Ka tapa zahtak kha ding uh hi,’ ci in a tawpna ah a tapa a paisak hi. 
\p 
\v 7 “Ahih hangin tua lokhawh thalawhte in, ‘Hihpa a innluah ding pa ahi hi. Hong pai un, amah that ni. Tua hi leh ama luah ding teng eite aa hong suak ding hi,’ ci in a kikum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 8 “Tua hi a, tua pa manin a thah khit uh ciangin lenggahhuan pualam ah a luang a pai uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 “Tua ahih ciangin lenggahhuan neipa in amaute bang a cih ding hiam? Amah hong pai in lokhawh thalawhte that ding a, lenggahhuan zong midangte a pia ding hi. 
\v 10 \x + \xo 12:10 \xt Saw 4:11\x*\w Lai Siangtho\w* sunga a kigelhna ah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Innlamte in a nilkhiat uh suang,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Innkiusuang bulpi a suak hi.\qt* 
\q1 
\v 11 \qt Hih in Topa sep hi a,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Eite muhna ah lamdang hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 12:11 \ft \+xt Lat 118:22-23\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a kici thu sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam?” a ci hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 12:12 \xt Mat 22:22\x*Amaute a kawkna in hih thugentehna a genlam thei uh ahih manin amah a mat sawm uh hi. Ahih hangin mipite lau uh ahih manin amah nusia in a paikhiamang uh hi. 
\s1 Phiangsiah Piakna 
\r Mat 22:15-22; Luk 20:20-26 
\p 
\v 13 \x + \xo 12:13 \xt Mat 22:16\x*Tua khit ciangin ama kammal tawh amah mawhmat dingin \w Pharisee\w* pawlte le Herod pawlte sung panin mi pawlkhat Zeisu kiangah a sawl uh hi. 
\v 14 Tua mite Zeisu kianga tun uh ciangin ama kiangah, “Sia aw, nang na thuman a, maitang zahtak tuam zong na neih loh banah kuamah dawm loin Pasian thu mantakin na hilh hi cih kong thei uh hi. \w Caesar\w* kumpipa tungah mimal \w siah\w* piak ding thukham tawh kituak hiam kituak lo hiam? 
\v 15 Pia ding ka hi uh hiam pia lo ding ka hi uh hiam?” a ci uh hi. 
\p Zeisu in amaute a kineihkhem ahihlam uh thei ahih manin, “Banghang in hong ze-et na hi uh hiam, \w denarius\w* tang khat hong la unla hong lak dih un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 16 Tua ciangin amaute in denarius tang khat hong paipih uh hi. Amah in, “Hih in kua lim le kua min ahi hiam?” a ci hi. 
\p Amaute in, “Caesar lim le min ahi hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 17 \x + \xo 12:17 \xt Rom 13:7\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “Caesar neihsate Caesar pia unla Pasian neihsate Pasian pia un,” a cih ciangin amaute in lamdang a sa mahmah uh hi. 
\s1 Thawhkikna Le Kiteenna 
\r Mat 22:23-33; Luk 20:27-39 
\p 
\v 18 \x + \xo 12:18 \xt Saw 4:1; 23:8; 1Co 15:12\x*Tua khit ciangin misite thokik lo hi a ci Sadduceete pawlkhat ama kiangah hong pai in thu dong uh a, 
\v 19 “Sia aw, Moses in laigelh a, \qt mi khat in ta nei loin a zi a sihsan leh a naupa in a zi luah henla, a upa aa dingin suan le khak tawi hen,\qt*\f + \fr 12:19 \ft \+xt Thu 25:5\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci hi. 
\v 20 Tu in unau pasal sagih a om uh hi. A upapen in zi nei a, suan le khak nei loin amah a si hi. 
\v 21 A nihnapa in tua nu teenpih a, suan le khak nei lo mahin a si hi. A thumna pa zong tua bangmah ahi hi. 
\v 22 A sagih un tua nu teenpih uh a, suan le khak nei lo vive in a si uh hi. A nunung pen in tua numei zong a si hi. 
\v 23 Tua ahih teh thawhkik ni ciangin hong thokik le uh tua numei kuapen zi in om ding ahi hiam? Banghang hiam cihleh a sagih un tua numei a teenpih uh hi,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 24 \x + \xo 12:24 \xt 2Ti 3:15-17\x*Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Lai Siangtho ahi a, Pasian vangliatna ahi zongin thei lo na hih manun na sangkhial uh hi. 
\v 25 \x + \xo 12:25 \xt 1Co 15:42, 49\x*Misite lak pan a thawhkik uh ciangin kuamah kipi kiteeng nawn lo ding uh a, vana om vantungmite a bang ding uh hi. 
\v 26 Ahi zongin misite thawhkikna tawh kisai in Pasian in Moses kiangah, \qt ‘Keimah in Abraham Pasian, Isaac Pasian, Jacob Pasian ka hi hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 12:26 \ft \+xt Pai 3:6, 15\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ci in sawlbawk kuang sung panin a genna thu Moses laibu sungah sim ngei lo na hi uh hiam? 
\p 
\v 27 “Pasian in misite Pasian hi loin a nungta mite Pasian ahi hi. Tua ahih manin na theikhial mahmah uh hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\s1 A Lianpen Thupiak 
\r Mat 22:34-40; Luk 10:25-28 
\p 
\v 28 \x + \xo 12:28 \xt Luk 10:25-28\x*Tua khit ciangin \w thukhamhilh siate\w* khat hong pai a, a thu kidotte uh hong za hi. Zeisu in thu kidongte kituak taka a dawnkik lianlian theih lam a zak ciangin Zeisu kiangah, “Thupiak teng lakah a lianpen bang ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 29 Zeisu in dawng a, “Thupiak teng lakah a lianpen in, \qt ‘Israelte aw, ngai un. Topa i Pasian in, Topa khat bek ahi hi.\qt* 
\v 30 \qt Na lungsim khempeuh, na nuntakna khempeuh, na ngaihsutna khempeuh le na hatna khempeuh tawh Topa na Pasian it in.’\qt*\f + \fr 12:30 \ft \+xt Thu 6:4-5\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* Hih in a lianpen thupiak ahi hi. 
\v 31 \x + \xo 12:31 \xt Thu 6:5; Mat 5:43\x*A nihna in a masa bang hi a, \qt ‘Nang le nang na ki-it bangin na vengpa na it in,’\qt*\f + \fr 12:31 \ft \+xt Thu 6:5; Mat 5:43\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* cih thupiak ahi hi. Hih thupiakte sangin a lianzaw thupiak a om kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 32 \x + \xo 12:32 \xt Isa 45:6, 14\x*Tua ciangin thukhamhilh siapa in, “Man mahmah hi, Sia aw, thuman thutak na gen hi. Pasian khat bek om a, \qt amah longal Pasian dang om lo hi.\qt*\f + \fr 12:32 \ft \+xt Thu 4:35\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\v 33 \x + \xo 12:33 \xt Siam 19:18; Thu 6:5; 1Sa 15:22; Hos 6:6; Mic 6:6-8; Heb 10:8\x*Mi khat in a lungsim khempeuh, a theihna khempeuh, a nuntakna khempeuh le a hatna khempeuh tawh Pasian it a, amah a ki-it bangin a vengpa zong a it ding ahi hi. Hih in \w haltum biakpiakna\w* le gangawh biakpiakna khempeuh sangin a thupi zaw hi,” ci in a gen hi. 
\p 
\v 34 \x + \xo 12:34 \xt Mat 3:2; Luk 20:40\x*Tua pa in pilna tawh a dawn lam Zeisu in a theih ciangin ama kiangah, “Pasian kumpigam tawh na kigamla kei hi,” a ci hi. 
\p Tua hun a kipan kuamah in thu a dong ngam nawn kei uh hi. 
\s1 Khazih Kua Tapa? 
\r Mat 22:41-46; Luk 20:41-44 
\p 
\v 35 \x + \xo 12:35 \xt Mat 26:55\x*Tua khit ciangin Zeisu in biakinnpi huang sungah thu a hilh laitakin, “Banghang in thukhamhilh siate in, Khazih in David Tapa hi ci thei uh ahi hiam? 
\v 36 \x + \xo 12:36 \xt 2Sa 23:2; Mat 22:44\x*David in Kha Siangtho theihsakna tawh a genna ah, 
\b 
\q1 \qt ‘Topa in ka Topa kiangah,\qt* 
\q1 \qt “Na galte na khengakna ka suahsak khit mateng in,\qt* 
\q1 \qt Ka taklam ah na tu in,” ci hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 12:36 \ft \+xt Lat 110:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m ci in a gen hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 37 \x + \xo 12:37 \xt Joh 12:9\x*“Tua hi a, David in amah Topa ci ahih leh bangci bangin ama tapa hi thei zel ding ahi hiam?” a ci hi. Mi honpite in lungdamtakin ama thugen a ngai uh hi. 
\p 
\v 38 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Thukhamhilh siate thuhilhna kidawm un. Amaute in puantualpi silhsa in vak kawikawi ding le sumbuuk khawng a zahtakna tawh hopih ding a ut uh hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 12:39 \xt Luk 11:43\x*Kikhopna innte ah tutna thupi tata le pawi annekna munah munhoih tata a deih uh hi. 
\v 40 Amaute in meigongte neihsa teng netum uh a, kineihtawmna tawh sawt pipi thu a ngen uh hi. Tua bang mite in a nasiazaw mawhsakna a thuak ding uh hi,” ci in thu a hilh hi. 
\s1 Meigongnu Sumpi 
\r Luk 21:1-4 
\p 
\v 41 \x + \xo 12:41 \xt 2Ku 12:9; Joh 8:20\x*Tu in sumpi khiatna kuang mai ah Zeisu tu in mite sumpi khiat a mu hi. Mi haute in sum tampipi a khia uh hi. 
\v 42 Tua ciangin a zawng meigongnu khat hong pai in dangka\f + \fr 12:42 \fk dangka\ft : A nunga Vantehnate nuai ah “quadran” en in.\f* tang khat tawh kikim sumnen tang nih a khia hi. 
\p 
\v 43 Zeisu in a nungzuite sam a, amaute kiangah, “Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, sumpi khiatna kuang sunga sumkhia khempeuh lakah hih a zawng meigongnu in tam a khia pen hi. 
\v 44 \x + \xo 12:44 \xt 2Co 8:12\x*Banghang hiam cihleh midangte in tampi a neih lak panin a khiat uh hi a, meigongnu ahih leh zawng napi in a kivak nading nangawn sit loin a neih khempeuh a khia hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 13 
\s1 Zeisu In Mailam Thu Genkhol 
\r Mat 24:1-2; Luk 21:5-6 
\p 
\v 1 Tua ciangin \w biakinnpi\w* huang sung pan Zeisu a paikhiat laitakin a nungzuite khat in, “Sia aw, en dih in hih suangte bangzahtakin gol a, hih innte bangzahtakin thupi ahi hiam!” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 2 \x + \xo 13:2 \xt Luk 19:44\x*Zeisu in, “Hih a lian mahmah innte mu hi lo na hi uh hiam? Hih suangte khat tungah khat nangawn kiciang nawn loin a kiphelkhia mang ding hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\s1 Hun Bei Ding A Lak Limte 
\r Mat 24:3-14; Luk 21:7-19 
\p 
\v 3 \x + \xo 13:3 \xt Mat 21:1\x*Tua khit ciangin biakinnpi lam nga in Olive Mual tungah Zeisu a tu hi. Tua laitakin Peter, James, John le Andrew in a tuamin thu a dong uh hi. 
\v 4 Amaute in, “Hih thute cik ciangin hong piang ding ahi hiam? Hih thu khempeuh a hong pian ding ciangin theihsakna lim bangbang a hong piang ding ahi hiam hong gen in,” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 5 \x + \xo 13:5 \xt Jer 29:8; Eph 5:6; 2Th 2:3; 1Ti 4:1; 2Ti 3:13; 1Jn 4:6\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute dawngin thu a genin ah, “Kuamah in note hong khem zawh loh nadingin kikem un. 
\v 6 Mi tampi in, ‘Keimah in Khazih ka hi hi,’ ci in keima minin hong pai ding uh a, mi tampi a khem ding uh hi. 
\v 7 Gal kidona thu le gal hong piang ding hi cih kamdawnte na zak uh hangin patau kei un; banghang hiam cihleh tua bang thute a piang ding mah hi a, ahih hangin beina a tung nai kei ding hi. 
\v 8 Banghang hiam cihleh minam khat le minam khat, kumpigam khat le kumpigam khat hong kido ding uh hi. Mun tuamtuam ah zin hong ling ding a, kialpi le buainate a hong tung ding hi. Tuate in nausuah natna tawh a kibang gimna kipatna ahi hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 13:9 \xt Mat 10:17\x*“Tua ahih manin na kikem un; banghang hiam cihleh amaute in thukhente tungah note hong ap in kikhopna innte ah hong sat ding uh hi. Keima hangin mangpite le kumpite mai ah hong kipuak ding a, tua in amaute tungah teci na pan theih nading uh ahi hi. 
\v 10 Minam khempeuh tungah lungdamna thu a kitangko masa ding hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 13:11 \xt Mat 10:19-20; Luk 12:11-12\x*Amaute in note hong manin zum ah hong puak uh ciangin bang ka gen ding hiam ci in lunghimawh masa kei unla bangmah zong ngaihsun khol kei un; banghang hiam cihleh a gen ding note hi loin Kha Siangtho ahih manin a hun liana hong piak bangbang in na gen un. 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 13:12 \xt Mic 7:6; Mat 10:21; Luk 12:51-53\x*“Tua ciangin unau khat le khat thah dingin a kilehhek ding uh hi. Pa in a ta lehhek ding a, tate in a nu le a pa langpan in thah a sawm ding uh hi. 
\v 13 \x + \xo 13:13 \xt Mat 10:22; Joh 15:21\x*Keima min hangin mi khempeuh in note hong mudah ding uh hi. Ahi zongin a tawp donga a kipte in hotkhiatna a ngah ding hi. 
\s1 Gimna Lianpi Hun 
\r Mat 24:15-28; Luk 21:20-24 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 13:14 \xt Dan 11:31; 12:11\x*“\w Lai Siangtho\w* a sim mi in thei tahen. Kamsangpa Daniel in a gensa ahi gam sung, \qt a lipkhaphuai siatna\qt*\f + \fr 13:14 \ft \+xt Dan 9:27; 11:31; 12:11\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* ama om nading mun hi lopi a, a hong ding na muh uh ciangin Judea gama om mite mual tung ah tai uh hen. 
\v 15 Innkhum zanga om mi in na khatpeuh la dingin inn sungah kumsuk in lut nawn kei hen. 
\v 16 Lokuante zong \w puan\w* la dingin ciahkik nawn kei uh hen. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 13:17 \xt Luk 23:29\x*Tua hun ciangin naupaite le nawine lai naungek a nei nupite a genthei mahmah ding uh hi! 
\v 18 Na tai hun uh phalbi laitak ahih khak loh nadingin thungen un. 
\v 19 \x + \xo 13:19 \xt Dan 9:26; Joe 2:2\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Pasian in na khempeuh a piansak cil a kipan tuni ciangdong a piang ngei nai lo, tunung ciangin zong a piang ngei nawn lo ding gimna, tua hun ciangin a piang ding hi. 
\v 20 Topa in tua nite a tomsak keileh kuamah a suakta zo kei ding hi. Ahi zongin a teelsa mite hangin tua nite a tomsak ding hi. 
\v 21 \x + \xo 13:21 \xt Luk 17:23\x*Tua hun ciangin mi khatpeuh in, ‘En in, hihlai ah Khazih om hi! En in, hualai ah Khazih om hi!’ a hong cih leh um kei un. 
\v 22 \x + \xo 13:22 \xt Joh 4:48; 2Th 2:9-10\x*Banghang hiam cihleh Khazih manlote le kamsang zuaute hong piang ding a, a teelsa mite nangawn a khem zawh uh leh a khem dingin limlamdangte le nalamdangte a piangsak ding uh hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 13:23 \xt 2Pe 3:17\x*Tua ahih ciangin kikem un. En un, hih thute khempeuh a pian ma in kong gen khinzo hi. 
\s1 Mihing Tapa Hong Pai 
\r Mat 24:29-44; Luk 21:25-36 
\p 
\v 24 “Tua gimna hun khit ciangin, 
\q1 ‘Ni hong mial ding a, 
\q1 Kha zong a tang nawn kei ding hi. 
\q1 
\v 25 \x + \xo 13:25 \xt Isa 13:10; 34:4; Joe 2:10; Mat 24:29\x*Vantung a aksite hong kia ding a, 
\q1 Vantung vangliatnate kiling ding hi.’ 
\p 
\v 26 \x + \xo 13:26 \xt Dan 7:13; Kil 1:7\x*“Tua ciangin \w Mihing Tapa\w* in vangliatna le minthanna lianpi tawh meii lakah a hong pai amaute in a mu ding uh hi. 
\v 27 \x + \xo 13:27 \xt Zec 2:6\x*Tua ciangin amah in a vantungmite sawl ding a, lei kiuli pan lei mong khat pan van mong khat donga om a teelsa mite a kaikhawmsak ding hi. 
\p 
\v 28 “Tu in theikung tawh kong gentehna panin hih thu na thei un. Theikung a hiangte meng a, a tehte hong sel ciangin khuakhal hong nai ta hi ci in na thei uh hi. 
\v 29 Tua mah bangin note in zong hih thute hong piang na muh uh ciangin tua hun kongbiang dongah hong tung ta hi ci in na thei un. 
\v 30 \x + \xo 13:30 \xt Luk 17:25\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, tulai khang mite a bei ma teitei in hih thu khempeuh a hong piang ding hi. 
\v 31 \x + \xo 13:31 \xt Mat 5:18\x*Van le lei a mangthang ding hi. Ahih hangin ka thute a mangthang peuhmah kei ding hi. 
\s1 A Ni A Nai Kithei Lo 
\r Mat 24:36-44 
\p 
\v 32 \x + \xo 13:32 \xt Saw 1:7; 1Th 5:1-2\x*“Ahih hangin a ni le a nai kuamah in a thei kei hi. Vana om vantungmite nangawn in thei loin Tapa in zong thei lo hi. Ahi hangin Pa khat bekin a thei hi. 
\v 33 A hun ding thei lo na hih manun kikem un. Pilvang unla thungen un. 
\v 34 \x + \xo 13:34 \xt Mat 25:14\x*Hih thu in khual gamlapi a a zinkhia ding mipa tawh kibang hi. Amah in a inn nusia in a nasemte tungah a innvai teng ap a, a nasep ding ciat uh zong a pia hi. Kong cingpa zong hoihtak a a cing dingin thu a pia hi. 
\p 
\v 35 “Tua ahih ciangin inn neipa in nitak ahi a, zankim laitak ahi a, aak masa khuan le zingsang phalvak ahi zongin bang hunin hong tung ding cih thei lo na hih manun kiging den un. 
\v 36 Tua hi keileh amah thakhatin hong tung ding a, na ihmut laitak uh hong tuak ding hi. 
\v 37 \x + \xo 13:37 \xt Luk 12:37\x*Note kiangah kiging den un kong cih mah bangin mi khempeuh tungah zong ka ci hi,” a ci hi. 
\c 14
\s1 Zeisu Thah Sawm Uh
\r Mat 26:1-5; Luk 22:1-6
\p
\v 1 \x + \xo 14:1 \xt Mat 12:14; Joh 11:55\x*Ni nih khit ciangin \w Paisan Pawi\w* le Silngo Sawhloh Anlum Pawi bawl hun a tung hi. Siampi liante le \w thukhamhilh siate\w* in zuauthu tawh Zeisu mana a thah theih nadingun lampi a zong uh hi.
\v 2 Ahih hangin amaute in, “Mi honpi hong so kha ding ahih manin pawikham sungin hih kei ni,” a kici uh hi.
\s1 Zeisu Sathau Kinilh
\r Mat 26:6-13; Joh 12:1-8
\p
\v 3 \x + \xo 14:3 \xt Mat 21:17; Luk 7:37-39\x*Bethany khua a miphak ngeipa ahi Simon inn sungah Zeisu an ne a a tut laitakin ama kiangah numei khat a hong pai hi. Tua nu in a manpha mahmah sathau namtui\f + \fr 14:3 \fk sathau namtui\ft : Himalaya muna po a nam nei singkung nam khat zung pan a kibawl hi hi.\f* \w suangkang thawl\w* khat hong paipihin a sukkhap khit ciangin Zeisu luzang ah a buak hi.
\p
\v 4 Tualai a om mi pawlkhatte lungkim lo uh a, “Banghang in hih numei in sathau namtui tuaci thangbawl ahi hiam?
\v 5 Zuak leng \w Denarius\w* 300 val bang man dinga, mi zawngte kipia thei ding hi,” ci in nakpi in a mawhsak uh hi.
\p
\v 6 Ahih hangin Zeisu in, “Tua ci omsak lel un; banghang in amah nawngkaisak na hi uh hiam? Amah in keima tungah nasep hoih khat a hong bawl ahi hi.
\v 7 \x + \xo 14:7 \xt Thu 15:11\x*Banghang hiam cihleh mi zawngte note tawh om den a, na ut hunhun un amaute tungah thupha na bawl thei ding uh hi. Ahih hangin kei ka hih leh note tawh ka omkhawm tawntung kei ding hi.
\v 8 \x + \xo 14:8 \xt Joh 19:40\x*Amah in ahih theih zahin a hih zo hi. A kivui ding ka pumpi sathau nuhin a hong pai ahi hi.
\v 9 \x + \xo 14:9 \xt Mat 24:14\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, hih lungdamna thu a kitangkona leitung mun khempeuh ah hih numeinu a kiphawk nadingin kei tungah a hong bawlna zong a kigen ding hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu A Lehhek dingin Judas Thukim
\r Mat 26:14-16; Luk 22:3-6
\p
\v 10 \x + \xo 14:10 \xt Mat 10:4\x*Tua ciangin sawm le nihte laka khat, Judas Iscariot in Zeisu lehhek dingin siampi liante kiangah a pai hi.
\v 11 Siampi liante in tua thu a zak uh ciangin lungdam uh a, sum piak dingin a kamciam uh hi. Judah in Zeisu a lehhek theih nading hun hoih a ngak hi.
\s1 Topa Nitak An
\r Mat 26:17-30; Luk 22:7-23; Joh 13:1-35; 1Co 11:23-25
\p
\v 12 \x + \xo 14:12 \xt Pai 12:1-11; Thu 16:1-4; 1Co 5:7\x*Tua ciangin Silngo Sawhloh Anlum Pawi kipat ni, Paisan tuuno a kigawh ni in a nungzuite in Zeisu kiangah, “Paisan Pawi an na nek nadingin koilai ah pai in hong bawlkholhsak le ung na ut hiam?” ci in a dong uh hi.
\p
\v 13 Amah in a nungzuite nih sawl a, “Khua sungah pai le uh teh tuibel a pua pasal khat tawh na kituak ding uh hi. Amah zui un.
\v 14 Ama lutna inntekpa kiangah, ‘Siapa in, “Ka nungzuite tawh Paisan Pawi an ka nek nading na zintunna inndei koilai ahi hiam?” ci un,’ a ci hi.
\v 15 \x + \xo 14:15 \xt Saw 1:13\x*Tua ciangin amah in inndei tungnung ah a za mahmah a kipuah a kibawlkholsa inndei khat hong lak ding hi. Tua sungah na bawlkhol un,” ci in thu a pia hi.
\p
\v 16 Tua ciangin a nungzuite paikhia uh a, khua sungah lutin Zeisu gensa mah bangin mu uh a, Paisan Pawi an a bawlkhol uh hi.
\p
\v 17 Nitak ciangin sawm le nihte tawh amah a hong pai hi.
\v 18 Tu in amaute tusukin an a nek laitakun Zeisu in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, keimah tawh an a nekhawm note lakah khat in nong lehhek ding uh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 19 A nungzuite khatem mahmah uh a, ama kiangah, “Kei ka hi hiam?” ci in khat khit khat a banbanin a dong uh hi. Tua ciangin a dang khat in, “Kei ka hi hiam?” a ci hi.
\p
\v 20 \x + \xo 14:20 \xt Joh 13:18-27\x*Amah in amaute kiangah, “Sawm le nihte lak panin kei tawh kuang sungah an a sawkkhawm mipa ahi hi.
\v 21 \x + \xo 14:21 \xt Mat 8:20\x*Mihing Tapa in ama thu \w Lai Siangtho\w* sunga a kigelhsa bangin a piang ding mah ahi hi. Ahi zongin Mihing Tapa a lehhekpa in gimna a thuak ding hi! Tua pa mihing in a piang vet lo hi leh ama aa dingin a hoihzaw ding hi,” ci in a dawng hi.
\p
\v 22 \x + \xo 14:22 \xt Mat 14:19\x*Amaute in an a nek laitakun Zeisu in anlum la a, lungdamna a koh khit ciangin balkham in amaute a pia hi. Amah in, “La unla ne un. Hih in ka pumpi ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 23 \x + \xo 14:23 \xt 1Co 10:16\x*Tua khit ciangin hai la a, lungdam a koh khit ciangin amaute a pia hi. Amaute khempeuh in tua hai panin a dawn uh hi.
\p
\v 24 \x + \xo 14:24 \xt Mat 26:28\x*Tua khit ciangin amah in amaute kiangah, “Hih in mi tampi aa dingin a luangkhia \w thuciamna\w* thak ka sisan ahi hi.
\v 25 \x + \xo 14:25 \xt Mat 3:2\x*Note kiangah a man takpi kong cihin ah, Pasian kumpigam sungah lenggahzu a thak ka dawn ni matengin ka dawn nawn kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 26 \x + \xo 14:26 \xt Mat 21:1\x*Amaute in biakna la khat a sak khit uh ciangin Olive Mual zuanin a paikhia uh hi.
\s1 Peter Nial Ding Kigenkhol
\r Mat 26:31-35; Luk 22:31-34; Joh 13:36-38
\p
\v 27 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah,
\b
\q1 \qt “~‘Tuucingpa ka sat ding a,\qt*
\q1 \qt Tuu honte a kithehthang ding uh hi,’\qt*\f + \fr 14:27 \ft \+xt Zec 13:7\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f*
\m ci in Lai Siangtho sungah a kigelh mah bangin, tu zan ciangin na vekpi un keima hangin na puk ding uh hi.
\b
\p
\v 28 “Ahih hangin ka thawhkik khit ciangin Galilee gam ah note ma in ka na paikhol ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 29 Peter in, “Mi khempeuh a puk zongin kei ka puk kei ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 30 \x + \xo 14:30 \xt Luk 22:34; Joh 13:38\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu in, “A man takpi kong cihin ah, tuzan aak nihvei a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 31 \x + \xo 14:31 \xt Luk 22:33; Joh 13:37\x*Peter in, “Nang tawh sihkhawm nading ahi zongin kong nial peuhmah kei ding hi,” ci in a khauhzaw in a gen hi. A dang teng in zong tua bangin a ci ciat uh hi.
\s1 Gethsemane Huan Sungah
\r Mat 26:36-46; Luk 22:39-46
\p
\v 32 Tua ciangin Gethsemane a kici mun khat a tung uh hi. Zeisu in a nungzuite kiangah, “Ka thunget kalin hihlai ah na tu un,” a ci hi.
\v 33 \x + \xo 14:33 \xt Mat 4:21\x*Amah in Peter, James le Johnte tonpih a, tualai ah a lungkham le a lungzin mahmah hun hong kipan hi.
\v 34 \x + \xo 14:34 \xt Joh 12:27\x*Tua khit ciangin amaute kiangah, “A si zo ding zahin ka lungsim gim lua mahmah hi. Hihlai ah om unla hong ngak un,” ci in thu a pia hi.
\p
\v 35 \x + \xo 14:35 \xt Mat 26:18\x*Amah a gamla zawdeuh ah pai a, lei ah bokin tua hun tawh a kipelh theih leh a kipelh nadingin thu a ngen hi.
\v 36 \x + \xo 14:36 \xt Mat 20:22; Rom 8:15; Gal 4:6\x*Amah in, “\w Abba\w*, Pa aw, nang aa dingin na khempeuh piang thei ahih manin hih hai tawh hong kipelhsak in. Ahi zongin kei deihna bang hi loin nangma deihna bang hi zaw tahen,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 37 Tua ciangin a nungzuite kiang a tun ciangin amaute ihmu in a om a mu hi. Amah in Peter kiangah, “Simon aw, ihmu na hi hiam? Nai khat sung nangawn hong ngak zo lo na hi hiam?
\v 38 \x + \xo 14:38 \xt Mat 6:13; Rom 7:22-23\x*Ze-etna sungah na lut khak loh nadingun thungenin kiging un. Lungsim a ut mahmah hangin pumpi a thanem hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 39 Amah va paikhiakikin thungen a, a nget ngei teng mah a va ngen hi.
\v 40 Hong kilehkik ciangin hak zo mahmah lo uh ahih manin ihmukik in a om uh a mu hi. Amaute in amah a dawn nading mel a thei kei uh hi.
\p
\v 41 \x + \xo 14:41 \xt Mat 26:18\x*A thumveina hong pai ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “lhmu mu lai in, tawlnga lailai ding na hi uh hiam? Phazo hi. A hun hong tungta hi. En un, \w Mihing Tapa\w* mawhneite khut sungah hong kilehhek ding hun hong tung zo hi.
\v 42 Tho unla pai ni. En un, kei hong lehhekpa hong nai mahmah ta hi,” a ci hi.
\s1 Zeisu Kiman
\r Mat 26:47-56; Luk 22:47-53; Joh 18:2-12
\p
\v 43 \x + \xo 14:43 \xt Mat 10:4\x*Amah tua banga a gengen laitakin sawm le nihte lakah khat ahi Judas le namsau le molhtum a tawi mi honpi thakhatin hong suak uh hi. Tua mite pen siampi liante, thukhamhilh siate le makaite sawl ahi uh hi.
\p
\v 44 Tu in a lehhekpa in, “Ka nap mipa amah ahi hi. Man unla lencip in paikhiatpih un,” ci in amaute theihsakna lim khat a piaksa ahi hi.
\p
\v 45 \x + \xo 14:45 \xt Mat 23:7\x*Amah a hong tun phetin Zeisu kiang naih a, “\w Rabbi\w*, Rabbi,” ci in a \w nam\w* hi.
\p
\v 46 Tua ciangin amaute in Zeisu manin a paikhiatpih uh hi.
\v 47 Ama kianga a ding mi khat in a namsau dokin \w Siampi Ukpa\w* nasempa a sat leh a bil a satkhia hi.
\p
\v 48 Tua ciangin Zeisu in amaute kiangah, “Guta buluh khat man ding bangin namsau le molhtumte tawi in kei hong man dingin hong kuan na hi uh hiam?
\v 49 \x + \xo 14:49 \xt Isa 53:7-12; Mat 1:22; 26:55\x*Nisimin \w biakinnpi\w* huang sungah thu hilhin note tawh ka om a, nong man kei uh hi. Ahih hangin Lai Siangtho a tangtun loh phamawh hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 50 Tua ciangin amaute khempeuh in amah nusia in a taikek uh hi.
\v 51 Tu in dialkang khat bek a silh tangvalno khat in Zeisu nung a zui hi. Mihon laka tangval dangte in tua pa a mat uh ciangin,
\v 52 tua pa in a dialkang nusia in a guaktangin a taikhia hi.
\s1 Biakna Makaite In Zeisu Thusit
\r Mat 26:57-68; Luk 22:54, 63-71; Joh 18:13-15, 19-24
\p
\v 53 Amaute in Siampi Ukpa kiangah Zeisu a paipih uh hi. Tua Siampi Ukpa kiangah siampi liante, makaite le thukhamhilh siate khempeuh a na kikaikhawm uh hi.
\v 54 \x + \xo 14:54 \xt Mat 26:3; Joh 18:18\x*Peter in Siampi Ukpa inntual dongin Zeisu galzuih a, tua munah biakinn cingte tawh tukhawm in mei a awi hi.
\p
\v 55 \x + \xo 14:55 \xt Mat 5:22\x*Tu in siampi liante le thukhente khempeuh in Zeisu thah theih nading teci a zon uh hangin khat beek a mu zo kei uh hi.
\v 56 Banghang hiam cihleh mi tampi in Zeisu langah zuau teci a pan uh hangin a tecipannate uh khat le khat a kituak kei hi.
\p
\v 57 Tua ciangin mi pawlkhat dingto in ama langah zuau teci a pang uh hi.
\v 58 \x + \xo 14:58 \xt Joh 2:19\x*Amaute in, “Hihpa in, ‘Khut tawh kibawl hih biakinnpi ka susia ding a, khut tawh kibawl lo a dang biakinnpi khat ni thum sungin ka lamkik ding hi,’ a cih ka za uh hi,” a ci uh hi.
\p
\v 59 Ahih hangin tua thu nangawn ah amaute tecipanna a kituak kei hi.
\v 60 Tua ciangin amaute laizang ah Siampi Ukpa dingto in Zeisu kiangah, “Kam khat beek dawng lo ding na hi hiam? Na langa hih mite tecipanna bang thu ahi hiam?” ci in a dong hi.
\p
\v 61 \x + \xo 14:61 \xt Isa 53:7; Mat 27:12, 14; Luk 23:9; Joh 19:9\x*Ahih hangin Zeisu in bangmah dawng loin a sip dide hi. Siampi Ukpa in, “Phatna a Ngahpa Tapa, Khazih na hi hiam?” ci in a dongkik hi.
\p
\v 62 \x + \xo 14:62 \xt Lat 110:1; Dan 7:13; Kil 1:7\x*Zeisu in, “Ka hi hi. Ahi zongin nang tungah kong genin ah, Vangliatna taklam ah Mihing Tapa tu in vana meiipi tawh a hong paina mailam ah na mu ding hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 63 \x + \xo 14:63 \xt Siam 10:6; Gam 14:6; Saw 14:14\x*Tua ciangin Siampi Ukpa in a \w puan\w* balkek a, “Teci dang bang kisam nawn i hi hiam?
\v 64 \x + \xo 14:64 \xt Siam 24:16\x*Pasian tunga a pausiatna na za zo uh hi. Bangci ngaihsut na hi hiam?” a ci hi.
\p Amaute khempeuh in, “Amah a si dingin kilawm hi,” ci in a mawhsak uh hi.
\v 65 \x + \xo 14:65 \xt Mat 16:21\x*Tua ciangin pawlkhat in amah cil a phih uh hi. A mai tunsak in tum uh a, “Kamsanna tawh hong gen dih in,” a ci uh hi. Biakinn cingte in zong a beng uh hi.
\s1 Peter In Zeisu Nial
\r Mat 26:69-75; Luk 22:55-62; Joh 18:15-18, 25-27
\p
\v 66 Inntual ah Peter a om laitakin Siampi Ukpa nasem numei khat ama kiangah a hong pai hi.
\v 67 Tua nu in mei-awi a om Peter a muh ciangin en a, “Nang zong Nazareth khua mi Zeisu pawl na hi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 68 Ahih hangin Peter in, “Na gen thu, ka thei kei a, zong ka tel kei hi,” ci in a nial hi.
\p Tua ciangin amah inn pualam zuanin paikhia a, aak a khuang hi.
\v 69 Tua ciangin tua nasem numei in amah va mukik a, a kianga a ding mite kiangah, “Hih mipa in amaute lakah khat ahi hi,” a ci hi.
\p
\v 70 \x + \xo 14:70 \xt Saw 2:7\x*Tua ciangin Peter in a nialkik hi. Tua zawh a sawt loin ama kianga a ding mite in, “Nangin amaute lakah khat na hi takpi hi. Galilee mi na hih lam na awkaihin kithei hi,” a cikik uh hi.
\p
\v 71 Ahih hangin Peter in, “Na genpa uh ka thei kei hi,” ci in amah le amah kihamsiat in a kiciam hi.
\p
\v 72 Tua ciangin a nihveina aak a khuang hi. Zeisu in, “Aak nihvei a khuan ma in thumvei nong nial ding hi,” ci in a gen thu Peter in phawkkik ahih manin a kapkhia hi.
\c 15 
\s1 Sanhedrin Mai Ah Zeisu 
\r Mat 27:1-2; Luk 22:66-23:1 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 15:1 \xt Mat 27:1; Luk 22:66\x*Zingsang tungin siampi liante in makaite, \w thukhamhilh siate\w* le thukhente khempeuh tawh thakhatin thu kikupna khat a nei uh hi. Amaute in Zeisu henin, paikhiatpih uh a, Pilate khut ah a pia uh hi. 
\s1 Pilate Mai Ah Zeisu A Kipuak Masakna 
\r Mat 27:11-14; Luk 23:2-7; Joh 18:28-38 
\p 
\v 2 \x + \xo 15:2 \xt Mat 2:2\x*Tua ciangin Pilate mangpipa in, “Nang Judah mite Kumpipa na hi hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p Zeisu in, “Na cih bangin ka hi hi,” ci in a dawng hi. 
\p 
\v 3 Siampi liante in thu tampi tawh a mawhmat uh hangin Zeisu in kam khat beek a dawng kei hi. 
\v 4 Tua ciangin Pilate mangpipa in, “Na langah hihzah taka hong kimawhmatna thu za khin na hih ciangin kam khat beek dawng lo ding na hi hiam?” ci in a dongkik hi. 
\p 
\v 5 Ahih hangin Zeisu in a dawn loh ciangin Pilate in lamdang a sa mahmah hi. 
\s1 Pilate Mai Ah Zeisu Nihvei A Kipuakna 
\r Mat 27:15-26; Luk 23:13-25; Joh 18:39-19:16 
\p 
\v 6 Tu in pawi hun ciangin Pilate in thongkiate lak panin amaute nget penpen mi khat a khahsak zel pen ngeina khat ahi hi. 
\v 7 Tua laitakin Barabbas a kici mi khat, kumpi a langpanpih a lawmte tawh thong sungah kol kibulh in a om hi. Amaute in kumpi langpang in mi a thatte ahi uh hi. 
\v 8 Tua ciangin mi honpite nakpitak kiko in Pilate in ahih ngei banga mi khat a khahsak nadingin a ngen uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 Ahih hangin Pilate in, “Judah mite Kumpipa hong khah leng na ut uh hiam?” ci in a dong hi. 
\p 
\v 10 Banghang hiam cihleh siampi liante in Zeisu a hazat manun ama kiangah a piakkhiat uh ahihlam Pilate in a thei gige hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 15:11 \xt Saw 3:14\x*Ahih hangin siampi liante in mi honpite hansuah uh a, Pilate in Barabbas a khah zawk nading a ngensak uh hi. 
\p 
\v 12 Tua ciangin Pilate in, “Tua ahih leh, Judah mite Kumpipa hi na cihpa uh bang kong cihsak ding deih na hi uh hiam?” a cikik hi. 
\p 
\v 13 Amaute in, “Amah khailum in!” ci in a kikokik uh hi. 
\p 
\v 14 Tua ciangin Pilate in amaute kiangah, “Banghang in khailum ding ka hi hiam? Amah in bang siatna bawl ahi hiam?” ci in a gen hi. Ahi zongin amaute in, “Amah khailum in!” ci in a kiko semsem uh hi. 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 15:15 \xt Isa 53:6\x*Tua hi a, Pilate in mi honpi a lungkim sak nadingin Barabbas khahsak a, Zeisu ahih leh a satsak khit ciangin khailup dingin a pia hi. 
\s1 Galkapte In Zeisu Zahko 
\r Mat 27:27-31; Luk 22:63, 64 
\p 
\v 16 \x + \xo 15:16 \xt Joh 18:28\x*Tua ciangin galkapte in \w mangpipa inn\w* ah Zeisu paipih uh a, galkaphon khempeuh zong a kaikhawm uh hi. 
\v 17 Amaute in \w puan\w* dupsan khat silhsak uh a, linglukhu a khusak uh hi. 
\v 18 Tua khit ciangin, “Judah mite Kumpipa aw, na ci dam tahen!” ci in a hopih uh hi. 
\v 19 \w Pumpeng\w* tawh a lutang satin cilphih uh a, khukdinin a bia uh hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 15:20 \xt Heb 13:12\x*A zahko khit uh ciangin puan dupsan pen suahkhiatsak in ama puan silhsakkik uh a, khailup dingin a paikhiatpih uh hi. 
\s1 Golgotha Ah Zeisu Kipaipih 
\r Mat 27:32-44; Luk 23:26-43; Joh 19:17-27 
\p 
\v 21 \x + \xo 15:21 \xt Mat 27:32; Luk 23:26; Rom 16:13\x*Tua laitakin Alexander le Rufus-te pa Cyrene mi Simon khualzin hong ciah tawh a kituak uh hi. Amaute in zawhthawhthu tawh amah manin Zeisu singlamteh a puasak uh hi. 
\v 22 Luguh Mun cih khiatna nei, \w Golgotha\w* kici munah amah a paipih uh hi. 
\v 23 \x + \xo 15:23 \xt Lat 69:21; Pau 31:6\x*Tua ciangin \w paknamtui kha\w* tawh kihel lenggahzu dawn dingin a piak uh hangin Zeisu in a dawn kei hi. 
\v 24 \x + \xo 15:24 \xt Lat 22:18\x*Amaute in Zeisu a khai khit uh ciangin a puante hawm uh a, amau tan ding ciat a theih nadingun lai-ai a san uh hi. 
\p 
\v 25 Tu in nai thum\f + \fr 15:25 \fk nai thum\ft : Zingsang nai kua cihna hi.\f* sat a, amaute in amah a khailum uh hi. 
\v 26 A lu tung sanah “JUDAH MITE KUMPIPA,” ci in mawhsakna lai khat a suang uh hi. 
\v 27 Guta nih zong a taklam ah khat, a veilam ah khat, amah tawh a khaikhawm uh hi. 
\v 28 Hih bangin, \w Lai Siangtho\w* sunga kigelh ahi, 
\b 
\q1 \qt “Thukham palsat mite tawh amah kisimkhawm hi,”\qt*\f + \fr 15:28 \ft \+xt Isa 53:12\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a cihna thu a tangtung hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 29 \x + \xo 15:29 \xt Lat 22:7; Joh 2:19\x*Tua mun a tawn kha mite in a lu uh peisan in a zahko uh a, “Hei! \w Biakinnpi\w* susia a ni thum sungin a lam kik ding pa aw, 
\v 30 nangmah kihonkhia inla, singlamteh tung pan hong kumkhia in!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 31 \x + \xo 15:31 \xt Lat 22:7\x*Tua mah bangin siampi liante le thukhamhilh siate in zong zahko in, “Hihpa in midangte hon zo napi amah le amah a kihonkhia zo kei hi. 
\v 32 I mit mahmah tawh mu a, i up theih nadingin Israel Kumpipa Khazih singlamteh tung panin tu in hong kumkhia hen,” a ci uh hi. 
\p Amah tawh a kikhaikhawm mite in zong a zahko uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Sihna 
\r Mat 27:45, 46; Luk 23:44-49; Joh 19:28-37 
\p 
\v 33 \x + \xo 15:33 \xt Amo 8:9\x*Tu in nai guk\f + \fr 15:33 \fk nai guk\ft : Sun nai sawm le nai nih cihna hi.\f* a kipan nai kua\f + \fr 15:33 \fk nai kua\ft : Nitak nai thum a cihna hi.\f* ciangdong leitung bup ah khim a zing hi. 
\v 34 Nai kua a sat laitakin Zeisu in, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabachthani?” ci in nakpi in a kiko hi. A khiatna in, 
\b 
\q1 \qt Ka Pasian, ka Pasian aw, banghang in hong nusia na hi hiam?\qt*\f + \fr 15:34 \ft \+xt Lat 22:1\+xt* pana kila ahi hi.\f* 
\m a cihna ahi hi. 
\b 
\p 
\v 35 \x + \xo 15:35 \xt Lat 69:21\x*A gei a a ding mite pawlkhat in a zak uh ciangin, “En un, amah in Elijah a sam ahi hi!” a ci uh hi. 
\p 
\v 36 Tua ciangin mi khat va tai a, tuihupna khat la in lenggahtui thuk a dimtakin a diah khit ciangin, pumpeng dawn ah suangin a dawn dingin tahto a, “Hi ci omsak tadih un. Amah lakhia dingin Elijah hong pai hiam, en dih ni,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 37 \x + \xo 15:37 \xt Joh 19:30\x*Tua ciangin Zeisu nakpitak kiko in a huu tawpna a sangkhia hi. 
\p 
\v 38 \x + \xo 15:38 \xt Heb 10:19-20\x*Tua laitakin biakinnpi sunga kideina puan kikek a, a lu panin a taw dong phelnih a suak hi. 
\v 39 \x + \xo 15:39 \xt Mat 4:3\x*Zeisu maingat a ding galkap 100 ukpa in amah tua bangin kiko a a huu tawpna a sankhiat a muh ciangin, “Hihpa in Pasian Tapa taktak ahi hi!” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 40 \x + \xo 15:40 \xt Lat 38:11; Luk 24:10; Joh 19:25\x*Numei pawlkhat in gamlapi pan galet uh a, tua numeite lakah Magdala khua mi Mary, James neuzaw\f + \fr 15:40 \fk neuzaw\ft : A dang James sangin nauzaw ahih keileh tom zaw cihna hi thei hi.\f* le Joses-te nu Mary le Salome-te zong a kihel uh hi. 
\v 41 \x + \xo 15:41 \xt Mat 27:55-56; Luk 8:2-3\x*Amaute in Galilee gam ah Zeisu a omlai in amah zui in a panpihte ahi uh hi. Jerusalem khuapi dong amah a zui numei dang tampi zong a om uh hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Kivui 
\r Mat 27:57-61; Luk 23:50-56; Joh 19:38-42 
\p 
\v 42 \x + \xo 15:42 \xt Mat 27:62; Joh 19:31\x*Tu in nitak hong hi a, tua ni in \w Sabbath\w* a tun ma \w Kigin Ni\w* ahi hi. 
\v 43 \x + \xo 15:43 \xt Mat 5:22; Luk 2:25, 38\x*Tua ciangin Arimathea khua mi Joseph in Pilate kiangah hangtakin va pai a, Zeisu luang a va ngen hi. Amah pen upa vaihawmte lakah mi thupi khat hi a, Pasian kumpigam a lamen mi khat zong ahi hi. 
\v 44 Zeisu si khin ahihlam Pilate in a zak ciangin lamdangsa mahmah a, galkap 100 ukpa samin a sih zawh bangtan sawt zo hiam ci in a dong hi. 
\v 45 Zeisu si khin hi cih thu Pilate in galkap 100 ukpa kiang pan a theihtel ciangin Zeisu luang Joseph a pia hi. 
\v 46 Tua ciangin Joseph in Zeisu luang lakhia a, a hoih mahmah puanpak khat lei in a tun khit ciangin suang kikhuak han sung khat ah sial a, suangtumpi khat khuk in hankong a khak hi. 
\v 47 Magdala khua mi Mary le Joses nu Mary-te in a luang kisialna mun a en uh hi. 
\c 16 
\s1 Zeisu Thokik 
\r Mat 28:1-10; Luk 24:1-12; Joh 20:1-18 
\p 
\v 1 \x + \xo 16:1 \xt Luk 23:56; Joh 19:39-40\x*Tu in \w Sabbath\w* ni hong bei a, Magdala khua mi Mary, James nu Mary le Salome-te in a luang zut nadingin sathau namtui a lei uh hi. 
\v 2 Nipikal sunga ni masa pen ni zingsang nisuah tungin daihawh dingin hanah a hong pai uh hi. 
\v 3 “Hankong khakna suangtum kua in hong honsak ding ahi hiam?” ci in a kikum uh hi. 
\p 
\v 4 Ahih hangin amaute a khuadak uh leh tua suangtum a kikhukkhiasa a om a mu uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh tua suangtum a lian mahmah khat ahi hi. 
\v 5 \x + \xo 16:5 \xt Joh 20:12\x*Han sungah lut uh a, puanpak tualpi a silh tangval khat taklam panga a tu a muh uh ciangin lamdang a sa uh hi. 
\p 
\v 6 Ahih hangin tua pa in, “Lamdangsa kei un. A kikhailum Nazareth khua mi Zeisu na zong uh hi. Amah thokik zo hi! Hihlai ah om nawn lo hi. A luang kisialna mun hong en un. 
\v 7 \x + \xo 16:7 \xt Joh 21:1-23\x*Tu in ciah unla Peter le a nungzuite kiangah, ‘Note pai ma in Galilee gam ah na paikhol ding a, a hong gensa bangin tualai ah amah na mu ding uh hi,’ ci in va gen un,” a ci hi. 
\p 
\v 8 Amaute han sung panin manlangtakin hong paikhia uh a, a tai uh hi; banghang hiam cihleh amaute lau uh a, lamdang a sa uh hi. Amaute lau uh ahih manin kuamah kiangah thu bangmah a gen kei uh hi. 
\p 
\v 9 \x + \xo 16:9 \xt Joh 20:11-18\x*Tu in nipikal khat sunga ni masa pen ni zingsang tungin Zeisu thokik a, dawi sagih a hawlkhiatna numei Magdala khua mi Mary kiangah a kilak masa pen hi. 
\v 10 Tua numei in Zeisu tawh a kithuah khawm ngei, dah le kap a om mite kiangah pai in tua thu a va gen hi. 
\v 11 \x + \xo 16:11 \xt Luk 24:11\x*Amah thokik ahihna le Mary in a muhna thu amaute in a zak uh ciangin a um kei uh hi. 
\s1 Emmaus Paina Lampi Tungah Zeisu Kilak 
\r Luk 24:13-35 
\p 
\v 12 \x + \xo 16:12 \xt Luk 24:13-32\x*Tua khit ciangin nungzuite nih gam sung khuaneu khat ah a pai laitakun amaute kiangah a nam tuamkhat in Zeisu a va kilak hi. 
\v 13 Amaute in nungzui dangte a va koh uh hangin a um tuan kei uh hi. 
\s1 Nungzuipite Tungah Zeisu Kilak 
\r Mat 28:16-17; Luk 24:36-43 
\p 
\v 14 \x + \xo 16:14 \xt Luk 24:36-43\x*Tua nung ciangin nungzui sawm le khatte an ne a a om laitakun amaute kiangah Zeisu a kilak hi. Amah a thawhkik khit cianga a mu mite thugente um loin lungkhauh uh ahih manin Zeisu in amaute a taii hi. 
\s1 Sawlna Lianpi 
\r Mat 28:18-20; Luk 24:44-49 
\p 
\v 15 \x + \xo 16:15 \xt Mat 28:18-20; Luk 24:47-48; Saw 1:8\x*Amah in amaute kiangah, “Leitung khempeuh ah pai unla a kipiangsak na khempeuh tungah lungdamna thu tangko un. 
\v 16 \x + \xo 16:16 \xt Joh 3:16, 18, 36\x*Thu umin tui a kiphum mi in hotkhiatna a ngah ding hi. Ahih hangin a um lo mi in mawhsakna a thuak ding hi. 
\v 17 \x + \xo 16:17 \xt Luk 10:17; Joh 4:48; Saw 5:16; 1Co 12:10\x*Thu-um mitetungah hih limlamdangte a piang ding hi. Keima min tawh dawite hawlkhia ding uh a, kampau thak tawh a pau ding uh hi. 
\v 18 \x + \xo 16:18 \xt Luk 10:19\x*Gulte man ding uh a, sih theihna gu a dawn uh hangin bangmah a ci kei ding uh hi. Cinate tungah khut a ngakh uh ciangin a dam ding uh hi,” a ci hi. 
\s1 Zeisu Van Ah Kilato 
\r Luk 24:50-53; Saw 1:9 
\p 
\v 19 \x + \xo 16:19 \xt Luk 24:50-51; Joh 6:62; Rom 8:34; Col 3:1; 1Ti 3:16; Heb 1:3\x*Tua bangin Topa Zeisu in amaute kiangah thu a gen khit ciangin vantung ah amah kilato a, Pasian taklam ah a tu hi. 
\v 20 \x + \xo 16:20 \xt Joh 4:48\x*A nungzuite kuankhia in mun khempeuh ah lungdamna thu a tangko uh hi. Topa in amaute tawh na semkhawm a, nalamdangte tawh ama kammal a kipsak hi. \w Amen\w*. 
